hadiths[197]{hadithnumber,text}:
1,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tamam aamaal ka daromadar niiyaton par hai, her shakhs ko wohi kuch milega jo usney niyat ki, pas jis shakhs ki hijrat Allah aur uskey Rasool ki khatir hui to uski hijrat Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khatir , aur jiski hijrat husoole-duniya ya kisi aurat se shaadi karney ki khatir hui to uski hijrat uski khatir hai jiski khatir usney hijrat ki .'' muttafaq aleh"
2,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab bayan kartey hain, ham eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke is beech main eik aadmi hamarey paas aaya, jiskey kapdey bahut hi safed aur baal intehai siyah they, is par safar ke aasaar nazar aatey they na ham mein se koi usey janta tha, yahan tak ke wo do zaanu ho kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney beth gaya aur usney apney dono haath apni raanon par rakh liye , aur kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! Islam ke mutalliq mujhey bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Islam ye hai ke tum gawahi do ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur ye ke Muhammad Allah ke Rasool hain, Namaz qaaim karo, Zakat ada karo, Ramazan ke rozey rakho aur agar istataat ho to Baitullah ka Haj karo.'' usney kaha : aapney sach farmaya , hamen is se tajjub hua ke wo aap se poochhta hai aur aap ki tasdeeq bhi karta hai, usney kaha : eman ke barey mein mujhey bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye ke tum Allah par , uskey farishton , uski kitabon , uskey Rasulon , aur yome-aakhirat par eman laao aur tum taqdir ke achcha aur bura honey par eman laao.'' usney kaha : aapney sach farmaya, phir usney kaha, ehsan ke barey mein mujhey bataeyn, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye ke tum Allah ki ibadat is tarah karo goya tum usey dekh rahey ho aur agar tum usey nahin dekh saktey to wo yaqinan tumhen dekh raha hai.'' usney kaha, qiyamat ke barey mein mujhey bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jawab denewala uskey mutalliq sawal karnewale se ziyada nahin janta.'' usney kaha, uski nishaniyon ke barey mein mujhey bata den. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye ke londi apni maalika ko janm degi aur ye ke tum nangey paaun, nangey badan, tang dast bakriyon ke charwaahon ko buland w baala imaraton ki taamir aur un par fakhr kartey huey dekhogey.'' umr ne farmaya : phir wo shakhs chala gaya, main kuch der thehra. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se puchha : '' umr ! kya tum jantey ho sawal karnewala kon tha ?'' maine arz kya, Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo Jibrael (Alaihissalam) they, wo tumhen tumhara Deen sikhaaney ke liye tumharey paas tashrif laye they.'' rawaahu Muslim (93)"
3,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera ne is hadees ko kuch alfaz ke ikhtilaf ke sath riwayat kya hai, is hadees mein hai : ''jab tum nangey paaon , nangey badan , behrey , gungey logon ko mulk ke badshah dekhogey , aur ye ( وقوع qiyamat ( paanch chizon mein se hai jinhen sirf Allah hi janta hai, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : '' be-shak qiyamat ka ilm Allah hi ke paas hai aur wohi barish nazil karta hai, '' , '' , .'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari w Muslim"
4,"Hazrat ibne-Umar bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Islam ki buniyad paanch chizon par rakhi gaee hai, gawahi dena ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. Namaz qaaim karna , Zakat ada karna , Haj karna aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhna .'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari w Muslim"
5,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''emaan ki sattar se kuch zayed shaakhen hain un mein se sab se afzal ye kehna hai ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin. aur sab se adnaa ye hai ke raastey se takleef deh chiz ko hata dena aur haya bhi eman ki eik shaakh hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari w Muslim"
6,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalman wo hai jiski zaban aur haath se musalman mehfooz rahen , aur Muhajir wo hai jo Allah ki mana ki hui chizon ko tarak kar dey .'' ye sahih Bukhari ki riwayat ke alfaz hain, jabkey sahih Muslim ki riwayat ke alfaz hain : farmaya ke kisi aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kya, kon sa musalman behtar hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jiski zaban aur haath se musalman mehfooz hon.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari w Muslim"
7,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi momin nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke main usey uskey walid , uski aulad aur tamam logon se ziyada mehbub na ho jaaun.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari w Muslim"
8,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs mein teen khaslatein hon usney unke zariey eman ki lazzat w halaawat ko pa liya, jis ko Allah aur uskey Rasool sab se ziyada mehbub hon, jo shakhs kisi se mehaz Allah ki raza ki khatir mohabbat karta ho, aur jo shakhs dobara kafir banna , uskey baad ke Allah ne usey us se bacha liya , aisey napasand karta ho jaisey wo aag mein dala jana napasand karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari w Muslim"
9,"Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ke rab honey , Islam ke Deen honey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Rasool honey par razi ho gaya usney eman ki lazzat ko pa liya .'' rawahu Muslim"
10,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai, is ummat ke jis Yahudi aur Esai ne merey mutalliq sun liya aur phir wo mujh par utaarey gaey Deen w shariyat par eman laye baghair faut ho jaey to wo jahannami hai.'' rawahu Muslim"
11,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen qism ke logon ke liye do ajr hain, ehle-kitab mein se wo shakhs jo apney Nabi par eman laya aur phir Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par eman laya , mamlook ghulam jab wo Allah ka haq ada karey aur apney malikon ka bhi haq ada karey, aur eik wo shakhs jiskey paas koi londi ho, wo us se ham-bistari karta ho, pas wo usey aadaab sikhaey aur achi tarah se adab sikhaey, usko behtareen zeware-taaleem se aarasta karey. phir usko azad kar dey aur uskey baad us se shaadi kar ley to uskey liye do ajr hain.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari w Muslim"
12,"Hazrat ibne-Umar bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey logon se qitaal karney ka hukm diya gaya hai. yahan tak ke wo gawahi den ke Allah ke siwa koi maboode-bar-haq nahin, aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, aur wo Namaz qaaim karen aur Zakat den, jab unka ye tarze-amal hoga to unhoney hudoode-Islam ke ilawa apni jaanon aur apney maalon ko mujh se becha liya, aur unka hisab Allah ke zimme hai.'' Bukhari, Muslim. albatta Imam Muslim ne '' hudoode-Islam'' ka zikr nahin kya. muttafaq aleh, Bukhari w Muslim"
13,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs hamari Namaz ki tarah Namaz padhey , hamarey qibley ki taraf rukh karey aur hamara zabiha khaye to wo aisa musalman hai jisey Allah aur uskey Rasool ki amaan hasil hai, so tum Allah ki amaan aur zimma ko na todo.'' Bukhari 391"
14,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera bayan kartey hain, eik dehati Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya, mujhey koi aisa amal bataeyn jiskey karney se main jannat mein dakhil ho jaaun . aapney farmaya : ''tum Allah ki ibadat karo aur uskey sath kisi qism ka shirk na karo, farz Namaz qaaim karo. farz Zakat ada karo aur Ramazan ke rozey rakho .'' usney kaha us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai ! main is mein koi kami beshi nahin karunga, jab wo chala gaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko pasand ho ke wo jannati shakhs ko dekhey to wo usey dekh ley.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 1397 w Muslim"
15,"Hazrat Sufiyan bin Abdullah Saqafi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)! mujhey Islam ke mutalliq koi aisi baat bataeyn ke main uskey mutalliq aap ke baad kisi se na poochhun, aur eik riwayat mein hai. aap ke siwa kisi se na poochhun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kaho main Allah par eman laya . phir Sabit qadam ho jaao .'' rawahu Muslim"
16,"Hazrat Talha bin Ubaidullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ehle-Najad se pareshan haal bikhrey baalon wala eik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua , ham uski aawaz ki gungunaahat sun rahey they lekin ham uski baat nahin samajh rahey they yahan tak ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qarib hua , aur wo Islam ke mutalliq poochhney laga , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' din aur raat mein paanch namazein .'' usney arz kya, kya unke ilawa bhi koi chiz mujh par farz hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, magar ye ke tum nafl padho .'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya .'' aur maahe-ramzan ke rozey .'' usney puchha : kya iskey ilawa bhi mujh par koi chiz lazim hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, siwaey iske ke tum nafli roza rakho.'' raawi bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey Zakat ke mutalliq bataya to usney kaha : kya uskey ilawa mujh par koi chiz farz hai? to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''nahin, siwaey iske ke tum nafli sadqa karo.'' raawi bayan kartey hain : wo aadmi ye kehtey huey wapis chala gaya : Allah ki qism ! main is mein kisi qism ki kami beshi nahin karunga, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya .'' agar usney sach kaha hai to wo kamiyab ho gaya.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 46 w Muslim"
17,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke jab abdul-Qais ka wafad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya .'' ye kon log hain ya kon sa wafad hai? '' unhoney arz kya : ham Rabeea qabeele ke log hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qom ya wafad ! khush aamadeed , tum kushada jagah aaye aur tum ruswa huey na naadim .'' unhoney arz kya aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham sirf hurmat waley mahinon mein aap ki khidmat mein hazir ho saktey hain, hamarey aur aap ke beech Muzar ke kuffar ka ye qabila abad hai, aap kisi faisla kun baat ke mutalliq hukm farma den taake ham apney pichley sathiyon ko uskey mutalliq bataeyn aur ham sab uski wajeh se jannat mein dakhil ho jaeyn . aur unhoney aap se mashrubat ke mutalliq puchha to aapney chaar chizon ke mutalliq unhen hukm farmaya aur chaar chizon se unhen mana farmaya , aapney eik Allah par eman laney ke mutalliq unhen hukm diya : '' farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke eik Allah par eman laney se kya murad hai? '' unhoney arz kya : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''is baat ki gawahi dena ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain. Namaz qaaim karna. Zakat ada karna aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhna, aur ye ke tum maale-ghanimat mein se paanchwan hissey ada karo.'' aur aapney unhen chaar chizon se mana farmaya, aapney badey matkon, kadu se baney huey piyaalon, lakdi se tarashey huey lagan aur tarkol se rangey huey roghni bartanon se mana farmaya , aur farmaya : ''unhen yad rakho aur apney pichley sathiyon ko unke mutalliq bata do.'' Bukhari, Muslim. hadees ke alfaz Bukhari ke hain. muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 53 w Muslim"
18,"Hazrat Ubaada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jabkey aap ke Sahaba kiram ki eik jamaat aap ke ird-gird thi. farmaya : ''tum is baat par meri baiat karo ke tum Allah ke sath kisi ko shareek nahin banaogey , tum chori karogey na zina karogey, tum apni aulad ko qatl karogey na apni taraf se kisi par bohtan lagaogey aur na hi maroof mein nafarmani karogey, pas tum mein se jo shakhs (ye ehad) wafa karega to uska ajr Allah ke zimme hai, aur jisney un mein se kisi chiz ka irtikab kya aur usey duniya mein uski saza mil gaee to uskey liye kaffara hai. aur jisney un mein se kisi chiz ka irtikab kya phir Allah ne uski parda poshi farmaai to uska mamla Allah ke sipurd hai. agar wo chahey to us se darguzar farmaai aur agar chahey to usey saza dey.'' pas hamne is par aap ki baiat kar li. muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 17 w Muslim"
19,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eidul-azha ya eidul-fitr ke moqe par eid-gaah ki taraf tashrif laye to aap khawatin ke paas se guzrey to farmaya : ''khawatin ki jamaat! sadqa karo, kyonkey maine jahannam mein tumhari aksariyat dekhi hai.'' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kis wajeh se ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : tum laan-taan ziyada karti ho aur khawind ki nashukri karti ho, maine tum se ziyada kisi ko Deen aur aql mein naqs rakhney ke bawajud pukhta raey mard ki aql ko ley janey wala nahin paya.'' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey Deen aur hamari aql ka kya nuqsan hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya aurat ki gawahi, mard ki gawahi se nisf nahin?'' unhoney kaha : ji haan, kyon nahin. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye uski aql ka naqs hai.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya jab usey haiz aata hai to us waqt wo Namaz aur roza tarak nahin karti?'' unhoney arz kya : kyon nahin, aisey hi hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye uskey Deen ke naqs mein se hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 304 w Muslim"
20,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala farmata hai : ibne-Adam ne meri takzeeb ki halanke ye uskey liye munasib nahin, aur usney mujhey bura-bhala kaha, halanke ye uskey laaiq nahin tha. raha uska mujhey jhutlana, to wo uska ye kehna hai ke wo mujhey dobara paida nahin kerega jaisey usney shuru mein mujhey paida kya tha, halanke pehli baar paida karna merey liye dobara paida karney se ziyada aasan nahin? aur raha uska mujhey bura-bhala kehna, to wo uska ye kehna hai : Allah ki aulad hai, halanke main yakta, be-niaz hun jiski aulad hai na waliden aur na koi mera ham-sar hai.'' (Bukhari 4974, 4975)"
21,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees mein hai : '' aur raha uska mujhey gaali dena , to wo uska ye kehna hai : meri aulad hai, halanke main us se paak hun ke meri biwi ho ya meri aulad ho.'' (Bukhari 4482)."
22,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala ne farmaya : ibne-Adam zamaney ko gaali deney ke baais mujhey takleef pahunchata hai, halanke main zamana hun, tamam maamlat merey haath mein hain, main hi din raat ko badlta hun.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 4826 , 7491 w Muslim"
23,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' takleef deh baat sun kar is par sabr karney wala Allah se badh kar koi nahin, wo uskey liye aulad ka daawa kartey hain, lekin wo phir bhi un se darguzar karta hai aur unhen rizq baham pahunchata hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 7378 w Muslim"
24,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechey gadhey par Sawar tha, merey aur aap ke darmiyan sirf paalaan ki eik lakdi thi, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Muaz ! kya tum jantey ho ke Allah ka apney bandon par kya haq hai? ''maine arz kya : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka bandon par ye haq hai ke wo uski ibadat karen aur uskey sath kisi ko shareek na banaeyn aur bandon ka Allah par ye haq hai ke wo us shakhs ko azab na dey jo uskey sath kisi qism ka shirk na karta ho.'' maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya main logon ko uski basharat na de-dun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen basharat na do warna wo (us baat par) tawakkul kar lengey .'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 2856 w Muslim"
25,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sawari par they jabkey Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke peechey bethey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Muaz ! '' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! farmanbardari ke sath hazir hun. aapney phir farmaya : '' Muaz ! '' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! farmanbardari ke sath hazir hun, aapney phir farmaya : '' Muaz ! '' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! farmanbardari ke sath hazir hun, teen martaba aisey hua phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs sachchey dil se ye gawahi deta ho ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, to Allah is par jahannam ki aag haram kar deta hai.'' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! kya main uskey mutalliq logon ko na bata dun taake wo khush ho jaeyn ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tab to wo tawakkul kar lengey .'' phir Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne gunah se bachney ke liye apni maut ke qarib uskey mutalliq bataya ."
26,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap safed kapda odhey so rahey they. mein phir dobara hazir hua to aap bedaar ho chukey they. tab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne ye iqrar kya ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin. phir wo usi par faut ho gaya. to wo jannat mein dakhil hoga .'' maine arz kya agar-che usney zina kya ho aur chori ki ho, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' agar-che usney zina kya ho aur chori ki ho.'' maine phir arz kya, agar-che usney zina kya ho aur chori ki ho? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' agar-che usney zina kya ho aur chori ki ho.'' maine arz kya, agar-che usney zina kya ho aur chori ki ho? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' agar-che usney zina kya ho aur chori ki ho. chahey Abu-Zar ko nagawar ho.'' Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) jab ye hadees bayan kartey to ye alfaz bhi bayan kartey they. agar-che Abu-Zar ko nagawar guzrey . muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 5827 w Muslim"
27,"Hazrat Ubaada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ye gawahi dey ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin, wo yakta hai, uska koi shareek nahin, aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. aur ye ke Esa (Alaihissalam) Allah ke bandey , uskey Rasool aur uski baandi ke bete hain, uska kalma hain jisey usney Maryam (Alaihissalam) ki taraf dala aur uski taraf eik rooh hain. jannat aur jahannam haq hain. Allah us shakhs ko jannat mein dakhil farmaeyga, chaahe uskey aamaal kaisey bhi hon.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 3435 w Muslim"
28,"Hazrat Amr bin Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain. main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine arz kya : apna daayan haath badhaayein taake main aap ki baiat karun, aapney daayan haath badhaya to maine apna haath khinch liya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Amr ! tumhen kya hua ?'' maine arz kya, main shart qaaim karna chahta hun, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bataao! kya shart qaaim karna chahtey ho?'' maine arz kya : ye ke mujhey bakhsh diya jaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Amr! kya tumhen malum nahin ke Islam pehley (haalate-kufr waley) gunah mita deta hai. hijrat apney se pehley kiye huey gunah mita deti hai aur beshak Haj bhi un gunahon ko mita deta hai jo us se pehley kiye hotey hain.'' aur Abu-Hurera se marwi (bayan) do hadisein , Allah Taala ne farmaya : ''main shurka ke shirk se be niaz hun.'' aur dusri hadees : '' kibr meri chadar hai.'' main un dono hadeeson ko inshaAllah taala ( '' baab riya'' (aur ( '' baab kibr'' ( mein bayan karunga. rawahu Muslim ."
29,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey koi aisa amal bataeyn jo mujhey jannat mein dakhil kar dey aur jahannam se door kar dey , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum ne eik bahut badi baat ke mutalliq puchha hai, lekin wo aisey shakhs ke liye aasan hai, jis par Allah Taala usey aasan farma dey , tum Allah ki ibadat karo aur uskey sath kisi ko shareek na banaao , Namaz qaaim karo, Zakat ada karo, Ramazan ke rozey rakho aur Baitullah ka Haj karo.'' phir farmaya : ''kya main tumhen abwaab khair ke mutalliq na bataaun ? roza dhaal hai, sadqa gunahon ko aisey mita deta hai jaisey pani aag ko bujha deta hai, aur raat ke oqaat mein aadmi ka Namaz padhna ( gunahon ko mita deta hai) .'' phir aapney ( Sura Sajda ki aayat ( tilawat farmaai : '' unke pehlu bistaron se door rehtey hain.'' yahan tak ke aapney '' wo amal kya kartey they, tak tilawat mukammal farmaai , phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen Deen ki buniyad uskey sutoon aur uski choti ke mutalliq na bataaun ?'' maine arz kya : kyon nahin, Allah ke Rasool ! zarur bataeyn , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Deen ki buniyad Islam hai, uska sutoon Namaz aur uski choti jihad hai.'' phir farmaya : ''kya main tumhen un sab se badi chiz ke mutalliq na bataaun ?'' maine arz kya : kyon nahin, Allah ke Nabi ! zarur bataeyn , aapney apni zaban ko pakad kar farmaya : ''isey rok lo .'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Nabi ! ham is se jo kalam kartey hain kya is par hamari pakad hogi? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Muaz! teri maa tujhey gum paey. logon ko unki zabanon ki kaat hi unke chehron ya nathnon ke baal jahannam mein giraaeygi.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 231, 22366 ( Tirmizi ( 2616 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3973 ( w Ahmed (5 / 236 , 237 , 247 ( ."
30,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne Allah ke liye mohabbat ki, Allah ki khatir bughz rakha, Allah ki raza ki khatir ata kya aur Allah ke liye rok liya to usney eman mukammal kar liya.'' rawahu Abu-Dawud (4681)."
31,aur Imam Tirmizi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Muaz bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se alfaz ki taqdeem w takheer ke sath usey yun riwayat kya hai : '' us shakhs ne apna eman mukammal kar liya .'' ( rawahu Tirmizi ( 2521 ( w sahi al-Hakim
32,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ki raza ki khatir mohabbat karna aur Allah ki raza ki khatir bughz rakhna aamaal mein sab se afzal amal hai.'' rawahu Abu-Dawud ( 4599 ( ."
33,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalman wo hai jiski zaban aur jiskey haath se musalman mehfooz rahen . aur momin wo hai jis se log apni jaanon aur maalon ke barey mein be khof aur pur-amn hun.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2627 ( w Nasai ( ۸ / ۱۰۴ , 105 padhi. 4998 ( w sahi ibne-Hibban ( al-ehsaan : 180 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 10 ( ."
34,"Hazrat Imam Behaqi ne Fazala aur Mujahid ki riwayat se ye izafa naqal kya hai : '' Mujahid wo hai jo Allah ki itaat ke barey mein apney nafs se jihad karey, jabkey Muhajir wo hai jo khataaon aur gunahon se kinara kaash! ho jaey.'' , ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 11123 ( w Ahmed ( ۶ / 21 , ۲۲ ح۲۴۴۵۸ , 24467 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3934 ( w sahi ibne-Hibban w al-Hakim (1 / 10 , ۱۱ ( ."
35,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bhi hamen khitab kartey to farmatey : ''jis shakhs mein amanat nahin uska eman hi nahin, aur jis shakhs ka ehad nahin uska koi Deen hi nahin.'' ( al-Behaqi fi shobil-emaan, ibne-Hibban ( al-ehsaan : 194 ( w ibn Khuzaima ( 3335 ( ."
36,"Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs gawahi dey ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain, Allah ne usko jahannam par haram kar diya hai.'' rawahu Muslim w Tirmizi ( 2638 )."
37,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ko is haalat mein maut aaye ke wo janta ho ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin to wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' rawahu Muslim w Tirmizi ( 1/45, 464, ibne-Hibban (201) ."
38,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do khaslatein do baaton ko wajib karti hain.'' kisi shakhs ne arz kya. Allah ke Rasool ! wo do wajib baatein kya hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ke sath shirk karta hua faut ho jaey, to wo jahannam mein dakhil hoga. aur jo shakhs is haal mein faut ho ke wo Allah ke sath kisi ko shareek na banata ho to wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' rawahu Muslim w Ahmed 3/ 391, 15270 ( ."
39,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain. ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ird-gird bethey huey they jabkey abu-Bakar w umr (Raziallahu anhu) Sahaba ki eik jamaat ke sath hamarey sath they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas se uth kar chaley gaey, aapney hamarey paas wapis aaney mein takheer ki to hamen andesha hua ke hamari ghair mojudgi mein aap ko koi takleef na pahunchaai jaey, pas ham (aap ki talash mein) uth khadey huye, to sab se pehla shakhs mein tha jo pareshan hua to main wahan se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko talash karney ke liye rawana hua , yahan tak ke main ansaar qabiley ke eik khandan banu-Najjaar ke eik baagh ke paas aaya to maine uska chakkar lagaya taake mujhey uska koi darwaza mil jaey lekin maine koi darwaza na paya , lekin wahan eik berooni kunwaan tha jis se eik naali baagh ki deewar se andar jati thi, pas main simat kar us raastey se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunch gaya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : '' Abu-Hurera ! '' maine arz kya, ji haan, Allah ke Rasool! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhen kya hua (ke yahan chaley aaye)?'' maine arz kya : aap hamarey paas tashrif farma they ke aap uth kar aagey aur hamarey paas wapis aaney mein takheer ki to hamen andesha hua ke hamari ghair mojudgi mein aap ko koi takleef na pahunchaai jaey, pas ham ghabra gaey, main pehla shakhs tha jo pareshani ka shikar hua, pas main us baagh ke paas pahuncha to main sikud kar us naaley ke zariey andar aa gaya jis tarah laumad sikud aur simat jata hai, aur wo log merey peechey hain, aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney jootey Mubarak mujhey de-kar farmaya : ''aey abu-Huraira! merey ye jootey ley jaao aur us deewar ke bahar aisa jo shakhs tumhen miley jo dil ke yaqin ke sath gawahi deta ho ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, to usey jannat ki basharat dey do.'' to sab se pehley umr (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat hui, unhoney puchha : Abu-Hurera ! ye dono jootey kaisey hain? maine kaha : ye dono jootey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hain. aapney ye de-kar mujhey bheja hai ke main aisey jis shakhs se milun jo dil ke yaqin ke sath gawahi deta ho ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, main usey jannat ki basharat dun, ( ye sun kar) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne merey seeney par maara to main peeth ke bal gir pada, unhoney kaha : Abu-Hurera wapis chaley jaao. main rota hua Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein wapis aaya, jabkey umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi merey peechey peechey chaley aaye , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Abu-Hurera ! tumhen kya hua ?'' maine arz kya : main umr (Raziallahu anhu) se mila to unhoney merey seeney par us zor se maara ke main peeth ke bal gir pada. aur kaha ke wapis chaley jaao, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Umar ! tumhen aisa karney par kis chiz ne aamada kya? '' unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! merey waliden aap par qurban hon, kya aapney apney jootey de-kar Abu-Hurera ko bheja tha ke tum jis aisey shakhs ko milo, jo dil ke yaqin ke sath gawahi deta ho ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, usko jannat ki khushkhabri suna do ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan '' unhoney arz kya : aap aisey na karen, mujhey andesha hai ke log is baat par tawakkul kar lengey aap unhen chhod den taake wo amal kartey rahen . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen (apney haal par) chhod do (taake amal kartey rahen ( .'' rawahu Muslim ."
40,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' is baat ki gawahi dena ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin jannat ki chaabii hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 242  22453 ( ."
41,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne wafat pai to aap ke Sahaba kiram aap ki wafat par gham zada ho gaey, yahan tak ke qarib tha un mein se baaz waswase ka shikar ho jatey , Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain aur main bhi unhi mein se tha, pas mein betha hua tha, ke is beech mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) paas se guzrey aur unhoney mujhey salam kya, lekin (shiddat gham ki wajeh sey) mujhey uska koi pata nahin chala, pas umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se shikayat ki, phir wo dono aaye yahan tak ke un dono ne eik sath mujhey salam kya, to abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aapney kis wajeh se apney bhai umr ke salam ka jawab nahin diya, maine kaha, maine to aisey nahin kya, to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : kyon nahin, Allah ki qism ! aapney aisey kya hai, Usman (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! mujhey na aap ke guzarney ka pata hai na salam karney ka, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Usman ne sach farmaya, kisi aham kaam ne aap ko us se ghafil rakha hoga? to maine kaha : aapney theek kaha, unhoney puchha : wo kon sa aham kaam hai? maine kaha : Allah Taala ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko wafat de-di is se pehley ke ham aap se us mamley ki najat ke barey mein daryaft kar letey, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine uskey mutalliq aap se poochh liya tha, main unki taraf mutawajjeh hua aur unhen kaha : merey waliden aap par qurban hon, aap hi uskey ziyada haqdaar they, abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine kaha : Allah ke Rasool ! us mamley ka hal kya hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne mujh se wo kalma, jo maine apney chacha par pesh kya lekin usney inkar kar diya, qubul kar liya to wohi uskey liye najat hai.'' rawahu Ahmed (1/20)"
42,"Hazrat Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah roey zamin ke her shehar w basti ke her ghar mein kalma Islam dakhil farma dega, chahey usey koi izzat ke sath qubul kar ley ya zillat ke sath zinda rahey, wo log jinhen Allah izzat ata farmaeyga to wo unko uska ehle (muhafiz) bana dega ya unko zaleel kar dega to wo uski itaat ikhtiyar kar lengey.'' maine kaha : goya Deen purey ka pura usi ka ho jaeyga. rawahu Ahmed (6/4  24315) w sahi ibne-Hibban al-Hakim ( 4 / 430 )."
43,"Hazrat Wahab bin Munabba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhen kaha gaya, kya «la Ilaah illallah ( ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin.'' jannat ki chaabi nahin? unhoney kaha : kyon nahin, lekin her chaabi ke dandaney hotey hain, agar tum dandaan wali chaabii laaogey to aap ke liye usey khol diya jaeyga, warna nahin khola jaeyga . Bukhari kitabul-janaeyz ( ."
44,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi apney Islam ko sanwaar ley to uska her nek amal das guna se saat so guna tak badha kar likha jaeyga, jabkey uski her burai utni hi likhi jaeygi yahan tak ke wo Allah se ja miley.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 42 w Muslim ."
45,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kya, eman kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : jab teri neki tujhey khush kar dey aur teri burai tujhey ghamgin kar dey to to momin hai.'' usney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! to gunah kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi chiz terey dil mein khatkey to usey chhod do.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 251 padhi. 22519 ( w sahi ibne-Hibban ( al-Mawarid : 103 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 14) ."
46,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! is Deen par aap ke sath aur kon hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' azad aur ghulam .'' maine arz kya : Islam kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' achi aur pakizah guftgu aur achcha khana khilana .'' maine arz kya : eman kya hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sabro- istiaqamat .'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : kon sa musalman afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jiski zaban aur haath se musalman mehfooz rahen.'' unhoney kaha, maine arz kya : kon sa eman afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' achey akhlaq .'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : kon si Namaz afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' lambey qiyam wali .'' wo bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : kon si hijrat behtar hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' to apney rab ki napasand chizon se kinara kaash! ho ja .'' unhoney kaha : maine puchha : kon sa jihad afzal hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya, '' jiskey ghodey ki taangein kaat di jaeyn aur usey Shahid kar diya jaey.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : kon sa waqt behtar hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' raat ka nisf aakhir .'' rawahu Ahmed (4 / 375  19655 ( w ibne-Maja ( 2794 w Muslim w al-Hakim (1 / 164 ( ."
47,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs is haalat mein Allah se mulaqat karey ke wo uskey sath kisi ko shareek na thehrata ho, paanchon namazein padhta ho aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhta ho to usey bakhsh diya jaeyga.'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! kya main unhen basharat na suna dun? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''unhen chhod do taake wo amal kartey rahen.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 232 padhi. 22378 ( w Tirmizi ( 2530 , 2531 ( w sahi al-Hakim (1 / ۸۰ ( ."
48,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se eman ki behtareen khaslat ke barey mein daryaft kya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Allah ke liye mohabbat karo, Allah ke liye bughz rakho aur apni zaban ko Allah ke zikr mein masroof rakho .'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! uskey baad kya karun ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum logon ke liye wohi kuch pasand karo jo apney liye pasand kartey ho aur unke liye us chiz ko napasand karo jisey apney liye napasand kartey ho.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 247 padhi. 22481 ( ."
49,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ke nazdik kon sa gunah sab se bada hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye ke to Allah ka shareek banaey halanke usney tumhen paida farmaya : '' usney kaha : phir kon sa ? aapney farmaya : ''ye ke to is dar sey apney bachey ko qatl kar dey ke wo tumharey sath khaeyga .'' usney arz kya : phir kon sa ? aapney farmaya : ''ye ke to apney padosi ki biwi se zina karey.'' Allah ne us masle ki tasdeeq mein ye aayat nazil farmaai : '' aur wo log hain jo Allah ke sath aur mabudon ko nahin pukartey aur jiskey qatl karney ko Allah ne haram qarar diya hai usey nahaq qatl nahin kartey aur na hi wo zina kartey hain.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6841 w Muslim ."
50,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke sath shareek banana , waliden ki nafarmani karna , qatle-nafs aur jhooti qism uthana kabeera gunah hain.'' (Bukhari 6675)"
51,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein jhooti qism ki bajaey jhooti gawahi ka zikr hai. muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 2653 w Muslim ."
52,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' saat mohlik chizon se ijtinab karo.'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! wo kya hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ke sath shirk karna , jadu karna , jiskey qatl karney ko Allah ne haram qarar diya hai, usey nahaq qatl karna , sood khana , yateem ka maal khana , ladaai ke din maidane-jihad se peeth pher kar farar hona aur paak daman aurton par tohmat lagana.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 2766 w Muslim ."
53,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis waqt zaani zina karta hai to wo us waqt momin nahin hota, jis waqt chor chori karta hai to us waqt wo momin nahin hota, jab wo sharab peeta hai to sharab noshi ke waqt wo momin nahin hota, jab lotney wala loot'ta hai to wo lootney ke waqt momin nahin hota jabkey log usey dekh rahey hotey hain aur jab khayanat karney wala khayanat karta hai to wo us waqt momin nahin hota. pas tum bach jaao, bach jaao.'' muttafaq aleh Bukhari 2475 w Muslim ."
54,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat mein hai : ''jis waqt qatil qatl karta hai to us waqt wo momin nahin hota.'' Ikrima bayan kartey hain, maine ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha is se eman kaisey nikal liya jata hai? unhoney farmaya : is tarah aur unhoney eik haath ki ungliyan doosrey haath ki ungliyon mein dalin aur phir unhen nikal liya , pas agar wo tauba kar ley to eman uski taraf is tarah lot aata hai, aur unhoney eik haath ki ungliyan doosrey haath ki ungliyon mein dalin, aur abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Raziallahu anhu)) ne farmaya : aisa shakhs kamil momin hoga na uskey liye Noore-emaan hoga.'' ye Bukhari ke alfaz hain. Bukhari 6809) ."
55,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''munafiq ki teen nishaniyan hain, jab baat karey to jhoot boley, jab wada karey, khilaf warzi karey aur jab uskey paas amanat rakhi jaey to khayanat karey.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 33 w Muslim. Imam Muslim ne alfaz zayed naqal kiye hain : ''agar-che wo roza rakhey, Namaz padhey aur wo musalman honey ka daawa karey.''"
56,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs mein chaar khaslatein hon wo khalis ( pakka ( munafiq hai, aur jis mein un mein se eik khaslat ho to is mein nifaq ki eik khaslat hai yahan tak ke wo usey tarak kar dey. jab uskey paas amanat rakhi jaey to is mein khayanat karey, jab baat karey jhoot boley, jab ehad karey to ehad shikni karey aur jab jhagda karey to gaali galoch par utar aaye.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 34 w Muslim."
57,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''munafiq ki misal us pareshan bakri ki tarah hai jo do rewadon ke darmiyan ho, kabhi wo uski taraf jati hai kabhi uski taraf.'' rawahu Muslim ."
58,"Hazrat Safwan bin Assaal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kisi Yahudi ne apney sathi se kaha : hamen us Nabi ke paas ley chalo , to usney apney sathi se kaha : tum Nabi na kaho : kyonkey agar usney tumhari baat sun li to wo bahut khush hoga, pas wo dono Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney wazeh nishaniyon ke barey mein aap se puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum Allah ke sath kisi ko shareek na banaao , na zina karo, na kisi aisi jaan ko jis ka qatl Allah ne haram qarar diya hai aur na kisi be-gunah shakhs ko kisi sahibe-iqtidar ke paas ley jaao ke wo usey qatl kar dey , jadu karo na sood khaao , paak daman aurat par tohmat na lagaao na ladaai ke din maidane-jihad se peeth pher kar bhago, aur tum bil-khusus yahood par lazim hai ke tum haftey ke din ke barey mein ziyadti na karo.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, un dono ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke haath aur paaon choomey aur kaha : ham gawahi detey hain ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Nabi hain, aapney farmaya : ''to phir kon si chiz tumhen meri ittiba nahin karney deti?'' unhoney arz kya : Dawud (Alaihissalam) ne apney rab se dua ki thi ke nabuwat ka silsila uski aulad mein jari rahey, aur ham dartey hain ke agar ham ne aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ittiba kar li to yahood hamen qatl kar dengey. rawahu Tirmizi ( 2733 , 3144 ( w Abu-Dawood w Nasai ( 8/ 111 padhi. 4083 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3705 ( ."
59,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen ( khaslatein ( eman ki asal buniyad hain, ( la Ilaah illallah ( ''Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin.'' ka iqrar karney waley shakhs ke dar-pe honey se ruk jana, kisi gunah ya kisi aur khilafe-sharaa amal ki wajeh se kisi ko Islam se khaarij mat karo, jihad jaari hai, jab se Allah ne mujhey Nabi banakar bheja hai, aur ye us waqt tak jari rahega jab is ummat ka aakhiri shakhs dajjaal se qitaal kerega, na kisi zalim ka zulm usey rok sakega na kisi aadil ka adl, aur taqdir par eman rakhna.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 2532 ( ."
60,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab banda zina karta hai to eman us se nikal kar chhatri ki tarah uskey sar par ho jata hai, jab wo us amal se ruju kar leta hai to eman bhi uski taraf palat aata hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi (2625 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 4690 ( w sahi al-Hakim (1 / ۲۲ ( ."
61,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey das chizon ka hukm detey huey farmaya, ''Allah ke sath kisi ko shareek na banana chaahe tujhey qatl kar diya jaey aur jala diya jaey, waliden ki nafarmani na karna chaahe wo tumhen hukm den ke to apney ehle w maal se alag ho ja, farz Namaz qasdan tarak na karna kyonkey jisney amadan farz Namaz tarak kar di to us se Allah ki aman khatam ho gaee, sharab na peena kyonkey wo her be-hayai ki buniyad hai, gunah se bachtey rehna kyonkey gunah Allah ki narazi ka baais banti hai, maidane-jihad se farar na hona chaahe log halak ho jaeyn, jab log (taaoon ki wajeh sey) maut ka shikar ho jaeyn aur tum un mein mojud ho to phir wahin raho, apni istataat ke mutabiq apney maal mein se apni aulad par kharch kar , adab sikhaaney ki khatir un se koi samjhauta na kar (maarney ki zarurat padey to maar) aur Allah ke barey mein unhen daratey raho.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 237 22425 ( w ibne-Maja ( 4034 ( ."
62,"Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, nifaq to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein tha, jabkey ab to kufr hai ya eman hai. (Bukhari 7114 ( ."
63,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah ne meri ummat ke dilon mein paida honey waley waswason se darguzar farmaya hai jab tak wo unke mutabiq amal na kar lein ya baat na kar lein .'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 2527 w Muslim ."
64,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke chand Sahaba Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unhoney aap se puchha : ham apney dilon mein aisey waswasey paatey hain ke unhen bayan karna ham bahut giraan samajhtey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum bhi aisa mehsus kartey ho ?'' unhoney arz kya, ji haan , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to sareeh eman hai.''"
65,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' shetan tumharey kisi shakhs ke paas aata hai to wo kehta hai : usko kis ne paida kya? usko kis ne paida kya? yahan tak ke kehta hai : terey rab ko kis ne paida kya? pas jab tum mein se koi us had tak pahunch jaey to wo Allah ki panah talab karey aur us ( shetani khayal ( ko chhod dey .'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 3276 w Muslim ."
66,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' log aapas mein sawal kartey rahengey yahan tak ke kaha jaeyga is makhluq ko to Allah ne paida farmaya hai to Allah ko kis ne paida kya? pas jo is tarah ki surat mehsus karey to wo kahe : main Allah aur uskey Rasulon par eman laya .'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 7296 w Muslim ."
67,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se her shakhs ke sath uska eik jin aur eik farishta sathi maamoor kar diya gaya hai.'' Sahaba ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath bhi ? aapney farmaya : ''merey sath bhi lekin Allah ne uskey khilaf meri madad ki to wo Mutee ho gaya, wo mujhey sirf khair w bhalai ki baat hi kehta hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
68,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' shetan insan mein khoon ki tarah gardish karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 2038 w Muslim ."
69,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Maryam aur unke bete ( Esa (Alaihissalam) (ke siwa aulade-Adam ke yahan paida honey waley her bachey ko shetan uski wiladat ke waqt chhoota hai to wo shetan ke chhedney par rotey huey cheekh maarta hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 2431 w Muslim ."
70,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab bachcha paidaish ke waqt cheekhta hai to uska ye cheekhnaa shetan ke kachokey ki wajeh se hota hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 4548 w Muslim."
71,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' shetan apna takht pani par sajaata hai. phir wo apney lashkaron ko rawana karta hai, wo logon ko gumrah kartey hain. un mein se uska ziyada muqarrab wo hota hai jo un mein sab se ziyada gumrah karnewala ho, un mein se eik aata hai to wo batata hai, maine ye-ye kya, to wo kehta hai, tuney kuch bhi nahin kya.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''phir un mein se eik aata hai to wo kehta hai, maine fulan ka peecha nahin chhoda yahan tak ke maine uskey aur uski biwi ke darmiyan judai dal di.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo (shetan ( usey apney qarib kar leta hai aur kehta hai : '' haan tum bahut khub ho.'' Aamash bayan kartey hain, mera khayal hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' to wo (shetan ( usey galey laga leta hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
72,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' shetan is baat se mayus ho chuka hai ke Jazeera Arab mein namazi uski puja karen, lekin wo unhen aapas mein ladaney ki koshish karta rahega.'' rawahu Muslim ."
73,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to usney arz kya : merey dil mein kuch aisa waswasa paida hota hai ke usey bayan karney se koila bin jana mujhey ziyada pasand hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka shukr hai jisney is mamley ko waswase mein badal diya.'' , (rawahu Abu-Dawud ( 5112 ( w Nasai fil-kubra ( 10503 ( w sahi ibne-Hibban ( 46 ( ."
74,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' shetan ibne-Adam ke dil mein khayal daalta hai aur farishta bhi khayal daalta hai. raha shetan ka waswasa dalna to wo shar aur haq ke jhutlaney ka wada deta hai, raha farishtey ka khayal dalna to wo khair aur tasdeeq haq ka wada deta hai, jo shakhs is tarah ka khayal mehsus karey to wo jaan ley ke ye Allah ki taraf se hai, pas wo Allah ka shukr ada karey, aur jo shakhs doosra khayal paey to wo shetan mardud se Allah ki panah talab karey.'' phir aapney ye aayat tilawat farmaai .'' shetan tumhen muflisi ka wada deta hai aur burey kaam ki targheeb w hukm deta hai.'' Tirmizi, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. ( rawahu Tirmizi ( 2977 ( w Nasai fil-kubra ( 11051 ( w ibne-Hibban ( ۴۰ ( Tabri fi tafseer ( 3 / 59 ( ."
75,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : '' log eik doosrey se sawal kartey rahengey yahan tak ke yun bhi kaha jaeyga is makhluq ko to Allah ne takhleeq kya, to Allah ko kis ne paida kya? jab wo ye kahin to tum kehna : Allah yakta hai, Allah be niaz hai, uski aulad hai na waliden aur na koi uska ham sar hai. phir teen martaba apni baain janib thook dey , aur shetan mardud se Allah ki panah talab karey.'' Abu-Dawood . aur ham Amr bin ahwas se marwi (bayan) hadees inshaAllah ( baab Khutba yoamun-nehar» mein zikr karengey .) rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 4721 , 4721 ( w Nasai fil-kubra ( 10497 , 661 ( ."
76,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' log eik doosrey se sawal kartey rahengey yahan tak ke wo kahengey , un sab chizon ko Allah ne paida farmaya , to phir Allah azz-w-jall ko kis ne paida kya? ''isey Bukhari ne riwayat kya. muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 7296 w Muslim . aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah azz-w-jall ne farmaya : aap ki ummat ke log is tarah kehtey rahengey, ye kya? usey kyon paida kya hai? yahan tak ke wo kahengey is makhluq ko to Allah ne paida farmaya to phir Allah azz-w-jall ko kis ne paida kya hai."
77,"Hazrat Usman bin abi al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! be-shak shetan merey, meri Namaz aur meri qirat ke darmiyan haael ho jata hai aur wo Namaz ko mujh par multabis kar deta hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo shetan hai usey khanzab kaha jata hai, pas jab tum mehsus karo to us se Allah ki panah talab karo aur teen baar apni baain janib thook do .'' ( wo bayan kartey hain ( pas maine aisey kya to Allah ne usey mujh se door kar diya .'' rawahu Muslim ."
78,"Hazrat Qasim bin Muhammad se riwayat hai ke kisi aadmi ne un se masla puchha to kaha : Namaz mein mera khayal kisi dusri taraf chala jata hai, aur aksar aisa hota hai. to unhoney kaha : apni Namaz jari rakho , kyonkey tumharey Namaz se farigh honey tak ye aatey rahengey , aur) Namaz ke ikhtitaam par) tum kahogey : maine apni Namaz mukammal nahin ki .) rawahu Malik (1 / 100  222 ( ."
79,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne zamin w aasman ki takhleeq se pachas hazar saal pehley makhluq ki taqdir likhi, aur uska arsh pani par tha.'' rawahu Muslim w taareekh Baghdad ( 2 / 252 ( ."
80,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her chiz yahan tak ke aajizi aur danai, taqdir ke mutabiq hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
81,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Adam aur Musa (Alaihissalam) ne apney rab ke yahan munaazra w mubaahasa kya, to Adam (Alaihissalam) Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib rahey, Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : aap Adam (Alaihissalam) hain jinhen Allah ne apney haath se takhleeq farmaya , us main apni rooh phunki, apney farishton se aap ko sajda karaya , aap ko apni jannat mein basaya phir aapney apni khata se logon ko zamin par utara , Adam (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : aap Musa (Alaihissalam) hain jinhen Allah ne apni risalat aur apney kalam ke liye muntakhab farmaya , aap ko takhtiyan ata kin jin mein her chiz ka bayan hai, aap ko kisi wastey ke baghair sargoshi ka sharf bakhsha , aap ke khayal mein meri takhleeq se kitna arsa qabl Allah Taala ne Torah likhi hogi ? Musa (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : chaalis baras , Adam (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : kya aapney is mein ye chiz bhi pai : Adam (Alaihissalam) ne apney rab ki nafarmani ki to wo bhatak gaey? unhoney farmaya : ji haan , Adam (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : kya aap mujhey aisey amal karney par malamat kartey hain jis ka karna Allah ne mujhey paida karney se bhi chaalis baras pehley mujh par lazim kar diya tha.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Adam (Alaihissalam) Musa (Alaihissalam) par ghalib aagey .''"
82,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jo ke sachchon ke sachchey hain, farmaya : ''tum mein se her eik ki takhleeq uski maa ke pet mein is tarah mukammal ki jati hai ke wo chaalis roz tak nutfa rehta hai, phir itni muddat jama hua khoon rehta hai. phir itni hi muddat gosht ka lothra rehta hai, phir Allah chaar baaten likhney ke liye uski taraf eik farishta bhejta hai, pas wo uska amal, uski Umr, uska rizq aur uska bad nasib ya saadat-mand hona likhta hai. phir is mein rooh phunk di jati hai. pas us zaat ki qism jiskey siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin, be-shak tum mein se koi shakhs ehle jannat ke se amal karta rehta hai yahan tak ke uskey aur jannat ke beech sirf eik haath ka fasla reh jata hai to wo navishtae- taqdir is par ghalib aa jata hai to wo jahannamiyon ka sa koi amal kar bethta hai to wo is mein dakhil ho jata hai, aur) isi tarah ( tum mein se koi jahannamiyon ke se amal karta rehta hai yahan tak ke uskey aur jahannam ke darmiyan sirf eik haath ka fasla reh jata hai to wo navishtae- taqdir is par ghalib aa jata hai aur wo ehale-jannat ka sa amal kar leta hai to wo is mein dakhil ho jata hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6594 w Muslim w Abu-Dawood ( 4708 ( ."
83,"Hazrat Sehal bin Saad (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : padhi. , banda jahannamiyon ke se amal karta rehta hai halanke wo jannati hota hai, doosra aadmi jannatiyon waley amal karta rehta hai, halanke wo jahannami hota hai, aamaal to wo ( qabile-aetbar ( hain jo aakhiri hain : ''muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6607 w Muslim."
84,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik Ansari bachey ke janaazey ki dawat di gaee to maine kaha : Allah ke Rasool! jannat ki us chidiya ke liye basharat hai, usney koi burai ki na uska waqt paya , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Aaisha ! kya uskey ilawa koi baat hai, be-shak Allah ne jannat ke liye kuch log paida farmaai , unhen jannat hi ke liye paida farmaya jabkey wo apney aabaa ki pusht mein they aur) isi tarah ( jahannam ke liye kuch log paida kiye , unhen jahannam hi ke liye paida farmaya jabkey wo apney aabaa ki peeth mein they.'' rawahu Muslim ."
85,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se her eik ki jahannam mein aur jannat mein jagah likh di gaee hai.'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham phir apney navishtae- taqdir par bharosa kar lein. aur amal karna chhod den ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' amal kartey raho , her eik ko , jis ke liye usey paida kya gaya hai, muyassar kar diya jata hai, jo shakhs saadat mandon mein se hoga to uskey liye ehale-saadat ke amal aasan kar diye jaeyngey, aur jo shakhs bad-nasibon mein se hua to uskey liye bd-naseebi waley amal aasan kar diye jaeyngey. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''jis kisi ne Allah ki raah mein diya aur darta raha, aur achi baat ki tasdeeq ki, to ham bahut jald uskey liye neki ki raah aasan kar dengey : '' ( muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 1362 w Muslim w al-Behaqi fi kitabul-qaza w qadr ( ۴۷ ( ."
86,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne aulade-Adam par uskey zina ka hissa likh diya hai, jisey wo zarur pa kar rahega , aankh ka zina dekhna hai, zaban ka zina bolna hai jabkey nafs tamanna aur aarzu karta hai aur sharm-gah uski tasdeeq ya takzeeb karti hai.'' aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : ''Allah ne ibne-Adam par uskey zina ka hissa likh diya hai, jisey wo zarur pa kar rahega , aankh ka zina dekhna hai, kanon ka zina sunna hai, zaban ka zina baat karna hai, haath ka zina pakadna hai, taang ka zina chal kar jana hai, jabkey nafs tamanna aur aarzu karta hai aur sharm-gah uski tasdeeq ya takzeeb karti hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6612, 6243 w Muslim ."
87,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke muzena qabeele ke do aadmiyon ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! log jo aaj amal kar rahey hain aur uskey liye mehnat w koshish kar rahey hain, kya ye aisi chiz hai jis ka faisla kya ja chuka hai aur pehley se jo taqdir hai wo nafiz ho chuki hai, ya wo us chiz ki taraf ja rahey hain jo unke Nabi unke paas lekar aaye aur unke khilaf hujjat qaaim ki ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin, balke ye eik aisi chiz hai jis ka unke mutalliq faisla ho chuka hai aur unke barey mein nafiz ho chuki hai, aur uski tasdeeq Allah azz-w-jall ki kitab mein hai : '' aur nafs ki qism ! aur uski jo kuch usney durust kya, phir bad-kari aur perhezgari dono ki usey samajh ata ki .'' rawahu Muslim ."
88,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! main jawan aadmi hun aur mujhey apney mutalliq zina ka andesha hai, jabkey merey paas shaadi karney ke liye kuch bhi nahin, goya ke wo aap se khassi honey ki ijazat talab kartey hain, raawi bayan kartey hain, aapney mujhey koi jawab na diya, phir maine wohi baat arz ki, aap phir khamosh rahey, maine phir wohi arz ki, aap phir khamosh rahey koi jawab na diya, maine phir wohi baat arz ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Abu-Hurera ! tum ne jo kuch karna hai ya tumharey sath jo kuch hona hai uskey mutalliq qalam likh kar khushk ho chuka ab uskey bawajud tum khassi ho jaao ya chhod do .'' Bukhari 5076 ( ."
89,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aulade-Adam ke tamam quloob (dil), qalbe-wahid ki tarah Rehman ki do ungliyon mein hain. wo jaisey chahta hai usey badlta rehta hai.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Allah ! dilon ko pherney waley ! hamarey dilon ko apni itaat par pher dena (yani Sabit qadam ( .'' rawahu Muslim ."
90,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' her paida honey wala bacha fitrat ( Islam ( par paida kya jata hai, pas uskey waliden usey Yahudi bana detey hain, ya usey nasrani bana detey hain ya usey majusi bana detey hain, jaisey janwer sahih Salim janwer ko janm deta hai, kya tum is mein se kisi ka kaan kata hua mehsus kartey ho?'' phir unhoney ye aayat padhi : ''ye wo fitrat hai, jis par Allah ne logon ko paida kya hai aur Allah ki us banai hui chiz mein koi tabdili na karo, yehi durust Deen hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 1358 w Muslim ."
91,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khadey ho kar hamen paanch chizon ke mutalliq khabar detey huey farmaya : '' be-shak Allah sota hai na ye uski shaan ke laaiq hai ke wo so jaey, wo meezan ko ooper nichey karta rehta hai. raat ka amal , din ke amal se pehley aur din ka amal raat ke amal se pehley , uski taraf pahuncha diya jata hai, uska hijaab Noor hai, agar wo us hijaab ko utha dey to uskey chehrey ke anwaar , wahan tak us makhluq ko jala den jahan tak uski nigah pahunchti hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
92,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka haath bhara hua hai, raat din ki sakhawat usey kam nahin karti , tum ne dekha ke usney zamin w aasman ki takhleeq ke waqt se jo kharch kya usney uskey haath ke khazaney mein koi kami nahin ki, aur uska arsh pani par hai, aur meezaan uskey haath mein hai wo usey past karta aur buland karta hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 4684 w Muslim . aur Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : ''Allah ka daayan haath bhara hua hai.'' ibne-Numair ne kaha : '' dono haath bharey huey hain. raat aur din ki sakhawat is mein koi kami nahin karti .''"
93,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mushrekin ki aulad ke barey mein puchha gaya, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' unke aamaal ke mutalliq Allah behtar janta hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 1384 w Muslim ."
94,"Hazrat Ubada-bin-Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne sab se pehley qalam ko paida farmaya to usey farmaya : ''likho. usney arz kya, kya likhun ? farmaya taqdir likho , usney jo kuch ho chuka tha aur jo kuch hona tha sab likh diya .'' Tirmizi, aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya , ye hadees sanad ke lihaz se gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 3319 , 2155 ( rawi ( 2329 ( ."
95,"Hazrat Muslim bin Yasar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se us aayat ke barey mein puchha gaya : ''jab terey rab ne bani-Adam ki pusht se unki aulad ko paida kya. '' to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab un se us aayat ke barey mein puchha gaya to farmatey huey suna : '' be-shak Allah ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paida farmaya , phir apna daayan haath unki pusht par phera to us se kuch aulad nikali aur farmaya : maine unhen jannat ke liye paida kya hai aur wo ehle jannat ke se amal karengey , phir unki pusht par haath phera to us se kuch aulad nikali to farmaya : maine unhen jahannam ke liye paida kya hai aur wo ehle jahannam ke se amal karengey .) ye sun kar) kisi aadmi ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! to phir amal kis liye karna hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah kisi bandey ko jannat ke liye paida farmata hai to usey ehle jannat ke aamaal par laga deta hai yahan tak ke wo ehle jannat ke se aamaal par hi faut hota hai Allah Taala us wajeh se usey jannat mein dakhil farma deta hai, aur jab wo kisi bandey ko jahannam ke liye paida farmata hai to usey jahannamiyon waley aamaal par laga deta hai yahan tak ke wo jahannamiyon waley aamaal par hi faut hota hai to wo us wajeh se usko jahannam mein dakhil kar deta hai.'' ( rawahu malik fil-Mota( 2 / 898 padhi. 1726 ( w Tirmizi ( 3075 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 4703 )"
96,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bahar tashrif laye to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke haathon mein do kitaben thin, aapney farmaya : ''kya tum jantey ho ke ye do kitaben kya hain ?'' ham ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! jab tak aap na bataeyn , ham nahin jantey , to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney daain haath wali kitab ke barey mein farmaya : ''ye kitab rabbul-aalameen ki taraf se hai, is mein jannatiyon , unke aaba aur unke qabeelon ke naam hain, phir unke aakhir par pura hisab kar diya gaya hai lihaza un mein koi kami beshi nahin ki ja sakti .'' phir aapney apney baaein hath wali kitab ke barey mein farmaya : ''ye kitab rabbul-aalameen ki taraf se hai is mein jahannamiyon, unke aabaa aur unke qabeelon ke naam hain, phir unke aakhir par pura hisab kar diya gaya hai lihaza is mein koi kami beshi nahin ki ja sakti .'' to aap ke Sahaba ne arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! jab faisla ho chuka hai to phir amal kis liye karna hai? aapney farmaya : '' miyaanaa rawi se durust aamaal kartey raho , kyonkey jannati shakhs se aakhiri amal jannatiyon wala karaya jaeyga, agar-che pehley usney kaisey bhi amal kiye hon, aur jahannami se aakhiri amal jahannamiyon wala karaya jaeyga, chahey us se pehley usney kaisey bhi amal kiye hon.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney haathon se wo kitaben rakh kar farmaya : ''tumhara rab bandon (ke maamley) se farigh ho chuka, pas eik giroh jannat mein aur eik giroh jahannam mein jaeyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2141 ( ."
97,"Hazrat abu-Khuzama apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha, maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! raahnumai farmaeyn, dam jiskey zariey ham dam karatey hain, dawaai, jiskey zariey ham ilaj kartey hain, aur bachaw ki chizen ( maslan dhaal waghera) jinkey zariey ham bachaw kartey hain. kya ye Allah ki taqdir se kuch rok sakti hain? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo ( asbab ikhtiyar karna ( bhi Allah ki taqdir mein se hain.'' rawahu Ahmed 3 / 421 padhi. 15551 , 15554 ( w Tirmizi ( 2065 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3437 ( ."
98,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham taqdir ke barey mein behes kar rahey they usi doran Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif ley aaye aur aap sakht naraz huey yahan tak ke aap ka chehra Mubarak surkh ho gaya goya aap ke rukhsaaron par anaar ke daney nichod diye gaey hain, to aapney farmaya : ''kya tumhen us ( taqdir ke masle par behes karney (ka hukm diya gaya, kya mujhey us chiz ke sath tumhari taraf bheja gaya hai? tum se pehli qomon ne us mamley mein behes w tanaaza kya to wo halak ho gaeen , main tumhen qism deta hun aur tum par wajib karta hun ke tum us masla par behes w tanaaza na karo.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2133 ( ."
99,Hazrat ibne-Maja ne Amr bin Shuaib an abi an Jadda ki sanad se isi tarah riwayat kya hai. rawahu ibne-Maja ( 85 ( .
100,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ko eik mutthi ( bhar mitti ( se jo usney sari satahe-zameen se hasil ki thi, paida farmaya. Adam (Alaihissalam) ki aulad zamin ( ki rangat ( ki munaasibat se paida hui, un mein se kuch surkh hain kuch safed aur kuch kalay aur kuch surkh w safed ke beech , kuch naram mizaj aur kuch sakht mizaj , kuch buri aadaat waley aur kuch pakizah sifaat waley.'' rawahu Ahmed (4 / 400 padhi. 19811 ( w Tirmizi ( 2955 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 4693 ( w sahi ibne-Hibban ( 2083 ( w al-Hakim ( 2 / 261 , 262 ( ."
101,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah ne apni makhluq ko andherey mein paida farmaya , phir un par apna Noor dala , pas jisko ye Noor muyassar aa gaya wo hidayat pa gaya aur jo us se mehroom raha wo gumrah ho gaya, pas main isi liye kehta hun, Allah ke ilm par qalam khushk ho chuka hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 2 / 176  6644 ( w Tirmizi ( 2642 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 1812 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 30) ."
102,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kasrat ke sath ye dua kya kartey they : dilon ko badalney waley ! merey dil ko apney Deen par Sabit rakhna , maine arz kya : Allah ke Nabi ! ham aap par aur aap ki shariyat par eman la chukey , to kya aap ko hamarey barey mein andesha hai? aapney farmaya : '' haan , kyonkey dil Allah ki do ungliyon ke darmiyan hain, wo jis tarah chahta hai unhen badlta rehta hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2140 ( w ibne-Maja ( 3834 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 526 ( ."
103,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' dil ki misal aisey hai jaisey kisi biyabaan mein koi (parinde ka ( par ho. jisey hawayen her aan ulat palat karti hon.'' (rawahu Ahmed (4 / 408 padhi. 19895 ( w ibne-Maja ( 88) ."
104,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi banda momin nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke wo chaar chizon par eman ley aaye , wo gawahi dey ke Allah ke siwa koi maboode-bar-haq nahin, aur main Allah ka Rasool hun, usney mujhey haq ke sath Nabi banakar bheja hai, wo maut aur maut ke baad zinda kiye janey par eman rakhta ho aur wo taqdir par eman rakhta ho.'' (rawahu Tirmizi ( 2145 ( w ibne-Maja (81) w ibne-Hibban ( al-ehsaan : 178 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 33) ."
105,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat ke do giroh aisey hain jinka Islam mein koi hissey nahin yani marjiya aur Qadriya.'' (Tirmizi : aur farmaya : ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 2149 ( w ibne-Maja ( 62 ( ."
106,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''meri ummat mein zamin mein dhans jana aur soorten badal jana hoga aur ye haal taqdir ko jhutlaney walon mein hoga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood 4613 ( w Tirmizi ( 2153 , 2152 ( w ibne-Maja ( 4061 )"
107,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Qadriya is ummat ke majusi hain, pas agar wo bimar ho jaeyn to unki iyaadat na karo aur agar wo faut ho jaeyn to unke janaazey mein na jaao.'' (rawahu Ahmed w Abu-Dawood ( 4691 )"
108,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' qadriyon ko apni majlison mein na bithaao na unhen salam karney mein pehal karo (aur na un se faisley karaao aur na hi un se munazra karo)'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 4710, 4720) w ibne-Hibban ( 1825 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 85) ."
109,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''6 qism ke logon par maine lanat ki aur Allah ne bhi un par lanat ki, aur her Nabi ki dua qubul hoti hai, Allah ki kitab mein izafa karney wala, Allah ki taqdir ko jhutlaney wala, taqat ke bal-bootey par musallat honey wala shakhs taake wo kisi aisey shakhs ko muazzaz banaey jisey Allah ne zaleel banaya ho, aur kisi aisey shakhs ko zaleel bana dey jisey Allah ne moazzaz banaya ho, Allah ke Haram ki be hurmati karney wala, meri aulad ki be hurmati karney wala aur meri sunnat ko tarak karney wala.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fil-mudkhal w rawahu fi-Shobil-Emaan (4010, 4011) w Tirmizi ( 2154 ( w ibne-Hibban (52) w al-Hakim (1 / 36 ( ."
110,"Hazrat matar bin Ukaam bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah kisi bandey ke mutalliq faisla farmata hai ke usey falan jagah maut aa jaey to wo us shakhs ke liye us jagah koi zarurat paida kar deta hai.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 227 padhi. 22332 ( w Tirmizi ( 2146 , 2147 ( w al-Hakim (1 / ۴۲ , 347 ( ."
111,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine arz kya, Allah ke Rasool! mominon ke bachey ( unke barey mein kya hukm hai) ? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' apney aaba ke sath hongey.'' maine arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! amal ke baghair hi , aapney farmaya : '' unhoney jo karna tha Allah us se b-khubi waqif hai.'' maine arz kya : to mushrekin ke bachchey? aapney farmaya : '' wo bhi apney aabaa ke sath, maine arz kya, amal ke baghair hi , aapney farmaya : '' unhoney jo karna tha, Allah us se b-khubi waqif tha.'' , ( rawahu Abu-Dawud ( 4712 ( w al-ajrii Suad 195  405 ( w Ahmed (4 / 76 ( ."
112,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' zinda dargor karney wali aur jiski khatir zinda dargor kya gaya jahannami hain.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 4717 ( w ibne-hibbaan (47) ."
113,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah azz-w-jall her bandey ki takhleeq se mutalliq uski paanch chizon , uski umr , uskey amal , uskey marney aur dafn honey ki jagah , uskey nuqoosh aur uskey rizq se farigh ho chuka .'' ( rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 197 padhi. 22066 , 22065 ( w ibne-abi Aasim fis-sunna ( 303 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 1811 ( ."
114,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' jisney taqdir ke mutalliq zara bhi baat ki to roze-qiyamat us se uskey mutalliq poochh-gachh hogi aur jisney uskey mutalliq koi baat na ki us se poochh-gachh nahin hogi.'' rawahu ibne-Maja (84) ."
115,"Hazrat Ibne-Delmi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main Ubai bin Kab ke paas aaya to maine unhen kaha : merey dil mein taqdir ke mutalliq kuch shubha sa hai, pas aap mujhey koi hadees sunaeyn, ummid hai Allah usey merey dil se door kar dey, to unhoney farmaya : agar Allah azz-w-jall aasman aur zamin walon ko azab dena chahey to wo unhen azab deney mein zalim nahin hoga, aur agar wo un par rehem farmaai to unke liye uski rehmat unke aamaal se behtar hogi, aur agar tum Uhud pahad ke barabar sona Allah ki raah mein kharch kar do to Allah usey qubul nahin kerega yahan tak ke tum taqdir par eman ley aao aur tum jaan lo ke jo kuch tumhen pahuncha wo tum se khata nahin ho sakta tha aur kuch tum se khata ho gaya wo tumhen pahunch nahin sakta tha, aur agar tum us aqidey ke ilawa kisi aur aqidey par faut ho gaey to tum jahannam mein jaaogey, ibne-dailmi bayan kartey hain, phir main ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya to unhoney bhi isi tarah farmaya : phir main Huzefa bin Yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein aaya to unhoney bhi yehi farmaya , phir main Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya to unhoney mujhey usi ki misl Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se hadees bayan ki.'' (rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 182 , 183 padhi. 21922 , 5 / 185  21947 w 5 / 189 padhi. 21992 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 4699 ( w ibne-Maja ( 77 ( w al-Behaqi fi kitabul-qaza w al-qadr 200 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 1817 ( ."
116,"Hazrat Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ibne-Umar ke paas aaya to usney kaha : falan shakhs aap ko salam kehta hai, to unhoney kaha : mujhey pata chala hai ke usney bidat ejaad ki hai, pas agar to usney bidat ejaad ki hai to phir meri taraf se usey salam na kehna, kyonkey maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''meri ummat mein ya is ummat mein , zamin mein dhansna, soorten maskh ho jana ya aasman se patharon ki barish hona hoga.'' Tirmizi, Abu-Dawud, ibne-Maja, Imam Tirmizi ne kaha : ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 2152 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 4613 ( w ibne-Maja ( 4061 )."
117,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Khadija (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se zamana jahiliyat mein wafat pane-waley apney do bachon ke barey mein puchha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' wo jahannam mein hain.'' raawi bayan kartey hain, jab aapney unke chehrey par nagawari ke asraat dekhey to farmaya : ''agar aap un dono ki jagah dekh lein to aap un se bughz rakhen .'' unhoney arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! aap se jo meri aulad paida hui hai? aapney farmaya : '' jannat mein .'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' momin aur unki aulad jannat mein , mushrik aur unki aulad jahannam mein .'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : '' aur jo log eman laye aur unki aulad ne eman laney mein unki perwi ki to ham unki aulad ko bhi unke sath mila dengey .'' rawahu Ahmed ( fi zawayed al-musnad 1 / 134 , 135 padhi. 1131 ( ."
118,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Allah ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paida kya to unki pusht par haath phera to unki pusht se wo tamam roohen , jinhen usney unki aulad se roze-qiyamat tak paida karna tha, nikal ayin , aur un mein se her insan ki peshani par Noor ka eik nishan laga diya, phir unhen Adam (Alaihissalam) par pesh kya to unhoney arz kya : merey parwardigar! ye kon hain? farmaya : tumhari aulad, pas unhoney un main eik shakhs ko dekha to uski peshani ka nishan unhen bahut achcha laga, to unhoney arz kya, merey parwardigar! ye kon hain? farmaya : Dawud (Alaihissalam), to unhoney arz kya, merey parwardigar ! aapney uski kitni umr muqarrar ki hai? farmaya : saath saal, unhoney arz kya : parwardigar! meri umr se chaalis saal usey mazeed ata farma dey.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Adam (Alaihissalam) ki umr ke chaalis baras baqi reh gaey to malakul-maut unke paas aaya to Adam (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya : kya meri umr ke chaalis baras baqi nahin rehtey? usney jawab diya kya aapney wo apney bete Dawud (Alaihissalam) ko nahin diye they? Adam (Alaihissalam) ne inkar kar diya, isi tarah uski aulad ne bhi inkar kya, Adam (Alaihissalam) bhool gaey aur us darkht se kuch kha liya, to ab uski aulad bhi bhool jati hai, aur Adam (Alaihissalam) ne khata ki aur uski aulad bhi khata kaar hai.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 3076 ( w al-Hakim ( 2 / 586 ( ."
119,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paida farmaya. jab unhen paida farmaya to Allah Taala ne unke daain kandhey par maara aur safed aulad ko nikala jaisey chewntiyan hon, aur usney unke baaeyn kandhey par maara to kaali aulad nikali jaisey koila ho, to Allah ne unki daain taraf walon ke mutalliq farmaya : ye jannati hain aur mujhey koi parwah nahin, aur jo unke baaeyn kandhey ki taraf they unke mutalliq farmaya : ye jahannami hain aur mujhey koi parwah nahin.'' (rawahu Ahmed ( 6 / 441 padhi. 27036 ( ."
120,"Hazrat abu-Nazara se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke abu-Adbullah naami sahabi bimar ho gaey to unke sathi unki iyaadat ke liye aaye to wo ro rahey they, unhoney kaha : aap kyon ro rahey hain? kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aap se ye nahin farmaya apni moochhein katraao , phir is par qaaim raho yahan tak ke tum ( hoze-kausar par) mujh se aa milo , unhoney kaha : kyon nahin. zarur farmaya tha. lekin maine Rasulullah ko farmatey huey suna : ''Allah azz-w-jall ne apney daain haath se mutthi bhari , aur doosrey haath se dusri , aur farmaya : ye us ( jannat (ke liye hai aur ye us ( jahannam (ke liye hai, aur mujhey koi parwah nahin .'' jabkey mujhey malum nahin ke main un do mutthiyon mein se kis mein hun.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 68  20944, 4 / 176  17736 ( ."
121,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne Arfa ke nazdik maqam Noman par aulad Adam se ehad leney ka irada farmaya to unki sulb se ( unki ( tamam aulad ko '' jisey paida karna tha, nikala to unhen unke samney bikher diya, jaisey chewntiyan hon, phir un se barahe-rast khitab kya to farmaya : ''kya main tumhara rab nahin hun? sab ne kaha : kyon nahin. ham is par gawah hain ( ye iqrar is liye liya gaya (ke kahin qiyamat ke din tum ye na kaho ke ham to is haqiqat se mehaz be khabar they, ya yun kaho ke shirk to hamarey aabaa ne kya tha, ham to unki aulad hain jo unke baad aaye , kya to hamen un ghalatkaaron ke kamon par halak kar dega .'' (rawahu Ahmed (1 / 272 padhi. 2455 ( w Nasai fil-kubra ( 6 / 347 padhi. 11191 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 27, 2 / 544 ( ."
122,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah azz-w-jall ke farman : ''jab aap ke rab ne bani-Adam se unki pusht se unki nasal ko nikala .'' ki tafseer mein farmaya : usney unko jama kya to unki mukhtalif asnaaf bana din, phir unki tasweer-kashi ki, unhen bolney ko kaha to unhoney kalam kya, phir un se ehad w meesaaq liya aur unhen unki jaanon par gawah banaya : ''kya main tumhara rab nahin hun?'' unhoney kaha : kyon nahin '' phir Allah Taala ne farmaya : main saaton aasmano, saaton zaminon aur tumharey baap Adam (Alaihissalam) ko tum par gawah banata hun ke kahin tum roze-qiyamat ye na kaho : hamen iska pata nahin, jaan lo ke merey siwa na koi mabud bar-haq hai na koi rab, merey sath kisi ko shareek na banana , main apney Rasool tumhari taraf bhejunga wo mera ehad w meesaaq tumhen yad dilaatey rahengey . aur main apni kitaben tum par nazil farmaaunga, to unhoney kaha : ham gawahi detey hain ke to hamara rab hai aur hamara mabud hai. terey siwa hamara koi rab hai na mabood, unhoney uska iqrar kar liya, aur Adam (Alaihissalam) ko un par zahir kya gaya, wo unhen dekhney lagey to unhoney ghani w faqir aur khoobsurat w bad-soorat ko dekha to arz kya, parwardigar! to ne apney bandon mein masaawaat kyon nahin ki, Allah Taala ne farmaya : main pasand karta hun ke mera shukr kya jaey, aur unhoney Anbiya (Alaihimussalam) ko dekha, un mein chiraghon ki tarah they un par Noor (baras raha) tha, aur un se risalat w nabuwat ke barey mein khususi ehad liya gaya, Allah Taala ke farman se yehi ehad murad hai, aur jab ham ne tamam nabiyon sey, aap sey, Nooh, Ibrahim, Musa aur Esa bin Maryam (Alaihimussalam) se ehad liya tha.'' Esa Alehissalam un arwaah mein they to Allah ne unhen Maryam (Alaihassalam) ki taraf bheja . Ubai (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya gaya ke us ( rooh ( ko Maryam (Alaihassalam) ke munh ke zariey dakhil kya gaya. ( rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 135 padhi. 21552 ( w al-Faryabi fi kitabul-qadr (52) w al-Hakim ( 2 / 323 padhi. 324 padhi. 3255 ( ."
123,"Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas bethey mustaqbil mein pesh aaney waley waqiyat ke barey mein baham (aapas mein) baat-cheet kar rahey they ke achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum kisi pahad ke barey mein suno ke wo apni jagah se hat gaya hai to is baat ki tasdeeq kar do. aur jab tum kisi aadmi ke barey mein suno, usney apni aadat badal li hai to uskey mutalliq baat ki tasdeeq na karo, kyonkey wo apni jibillat par kar-band rahega.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 6 / 443 padhi. 28047)."
124,"Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai, unhoney arz kya : Allah ke Rasool! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo zahar aalud bakri khai thi uski wajeh se aap her saal takleef mehsus kartey hain. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey us se jo bhi takleef pahunchi hai wo to merey mutalliq us waqt likh di gaee thi jab Adam (Alaihissalam) abhi mitti ki surat mein they.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ( 3546 ( ."
125,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu), Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab musalman se qabr mein (uskey rab, Nabi aur Deen ke barey mein) sawal kya jaey wo gawahi deta hai ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Allah ke Rasool hain. ye kehna Allah ke us farman ke mutabiq hai : ''Allah un logon ko jo eman latey hain sachi baat par duniya w aakhirat mein Sabit qadam rakhta hai.'' aur eik riwayat mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se marwi (bayan) hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ( یُثَبّتُ اللہُ الَّذِیْنَ امَنُوا بِالْقَوْلِ الثَّبِتِ فِی الْحَیَاۃِ الدُّنْیَا وَ فِی الْاٰخِرَۃِ ( azabe-qabr ke barey mein nazil hui, puchha jaeyga : tera rab kon hai? to wo kaheyga : mera rab Allah hai aur merey Nabi Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain.''"
126,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab bandey ko uski qabr mein rakh diya jata hai, aur uskey sathi wapis chaley jatey hain, to wo unke jooton ki aawaz sunta hai. (usi beech mein) do farishtey uskey paas aatey hain to wo usey bitha kar poochhtey hain : tum us shakhs Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke barey mein kya kaha kartey they? jo momin hai, to wo kehta hai : main gawahi deta hun ke wo Allah ke bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. usey kaha jata hai : jahannam mein apney thikaney ko dekh lo, Allah ne uskey badley main tumhen jannat mein thikana dey diya hai. wo un dono ko eik sath dekhta hai, raha munafiq w kafir shakhs, to usey bhi kaha jata hai. tum us shakhs ke barey mein kya kaha kartey they? to wo kehta hai : main nahin janta, mein wohi kuch kehta tha jo log kaha kartey they, usey kaha jaeyga : tum ne (haq baat) samajhney ki koshish ki na padhney ki, usey lohey ke hathodon ke sath eik sath maara jaeyga to wo cheekhta chalata hai jisey jin w Anas ke siwa uskey qarib her chiz sunti hai.'' Bukhari, Muslim. aur ye alfaz Bukhari ke hain. muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 1374 w Muslim."
127,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi shakhs faut ho jata hai. to subh w Sham uska thikana usey dikhaya jata hai. agar to wo jannati hai to wo ehale-jannat se hai, aur agar wo jahannami hai to phir wo ehle jahannam mein se hai, pas usey kaha jaeyga : ye tumhara thikana hai yahan tak ke Allah qiyamat ke din tumhen uskey liye dobara zinda kerega.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 1379 w Muslim."
128,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke eik Yahudi aurat unke paas aai to usney azabe-qabr ka zikr kya aur un se kaha : Allah aap ko azabe-qabr se bachaey , Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne azabe-qabr ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha to aapney farmaya : ''haan, azabe-qabr hai.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, maine dekha ke aap uskey baad jab bhi Namaz padhtey to azabe-qabr se Allah ki panah talab kartey they. muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 1372 w Muslim ."
129,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, is beech mein ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney khachar par Sawaar banu-Najjaar ke baagh mein they jabkey ham bhi aap ke sath they ke achcha khachar bidka, qarib tha ke wo aap ko gira deta , wahan paanch , chhe qabren thin . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' un qabron walon ko kon janta hai? '' eik aadmi ne arz kya, main : aapney farmaya : '' wo Kab faut huey they ?'' usney kaha : haalate-shirk mein , aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak is ummat ke logon ka unki qabron mein imtihan liya jaeyga, agar aisey na hota ke tum dafn karna chhod dogey to main Allah se dua karta ke wo azabe-qabr tumhen suna dey jo main sun raha hun, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna rukhe-anwar hamari taraf kartey huey farmaya : ''jahannam ke azab se Allah ki panah talab karo.'' unhoney arz kya : ham azabe-jahannam se Allah ki panah talab kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''azabe-qabr se Allah ki panah talab karo.'' unhoney kaha : ham azabe-qabr se Allah ki panah talab kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''zahiri w batni fitnon se Allah ki panah talab karo.'' unhoney kaha : ham zahiri w batni fitnon se Allah ki panah chahtey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' dajjaal ke fitne se Allah ki panah talab karo.'' unhoney kaha : ham dajjaal ke fitne se Allah ki panah chahtey hain.'' rawahu Muslim."
130,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab maiyat ko qabr mein dafn kar diya jata hai. to siyah faam neeli aakhon waley do farishtey uskey paas aatey hain, un mein se eik ko munkar aur doosrey ko nakeer kehtey hain. pas wo kehtey hain? tum us shakhs ke barey mein kya kaha kartey they? to wo kehta hai : wo Allah ke bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi mabud bar-haq nahin aur ye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey bandey aur uskey Rasool hain. wo dono farishtey kehtey hain : hamen pata tha ke tum yehi kahogey, phir uski qabr ko lambaai-chaudaai mein sattar sattar haath kushada kar diya jata hai, phir uskey liye is mein roshni kar di jati hai, phir usey kaha jata hai : so jaao, wo kehta hai : main apney ghar walon ke paas wapis jana chahta hun taake unhen bata aaun, lekin wo kehtey hain dulhan ki tarah so ja, jisey uskey ghar ka aziz tareen fard hi bedar karta hai, yahan tak ke Allah usey uski khuwabgaah se bedaar kerega, aur agar wo munafiq hua to wo kahega : maine logon ko eik baat kartey huey suna, to maine bhi wesay hi keh diya, main kuch nahin janta, wo farishtey kehtey hain : hamen pata tha ke tum yehi kahogey, pas zamin se kaha jata hai is par tang ho ja, wo is par tang ho jati hai. us se uski udhar ki pasliyan udhar aa jaeyngi, pas usey is mein musalsal azab hota rahega yahan tak ke Allah uski us khuwab gaah se usey dobara zinda kerega.'' (rawahu Tirmizi ( 1071 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 3107 ( ."
131,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''do farishtey uskey paas aatey hain, to usey bitha kar poochhtey hain, tera rab kon hai? to wo kehta hai : mera rab Allah hai, phir wo poochhtey hain : tera Deen kya hai? to wo kehta hai : mera Deen Islam hai, phir wo poochhtey hain : ye aadmi jo tum mein Nabi banakar bheje gaey they, wo kon they? wo jawab dega wo Allah ke Rasool hain, wo dono farishtey kehtey hain : tumhen kis ne bataya? wo kehta hai : maine Allah ki kitab padhi, to main is par eman ley aaya aur tasdeeq ki, uska ye jawab dena Allah Taala ke us farman ke mutabiq hai : ''Allah un logon ko jo eman latey hain, sachi baat par Sabit qadam rakhta hai.'' farmaya : aasman se aawaz deney wala aawaz deta hai : merey bandey ne sach kaha, usey jannati bichona bicha do, jannati libas pehna do aur uskey liye jannat ki taraf eik darwaza khol do, wo khol diya jata hai, wahan se khushbudaar hawa ka jhonka uskey paas aata hai, aur uski hade-nigah tak uski qabr kushada kar di jati hai, phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kafir ki maut ka zikr kartey huey farmaya : uski rooh ko uskey jism mein lotaya jata hai, do farishtey uskey paas aatey hain, to wo usey bitha kar poochhtey hain : tera rab kon hai? wo kehta hai : haaye ! haaye ! main nahin janta , phir wo poochhtey hain : tera Deen kya hai? wo jawab deta hai : haaye ! haaye ! main nahin janta , phir wo poochhtey hain : wo shakhs jo tum mein Nabi banakar bhejey gaey they, kon they? phir wohi jawab deta hai : haaye ! haaye ! main nahin janta, aasman se aawaz deney wala aawaz deta hai : usney jhoot bola, lihaza usey jahannam se bistar bicha do. jahannam se libas pehna do aur uskey liye jahannam ki taraf eik darwaza khol do, farmaya : jahannam ki haraarat aur wahan ki garm lu us tak pahunchegi, farmaya : uski qabr is par tang kar di jati hai, yahan tak ke uski udhar ki pasliyaan udhar nikal jati hain. phir eik andha aur behra darogha is par musallat kar diya jata hai. jiskey paas lohey ka bada hathoda hota hai, agar usey pahad par maara jaey to wo mitti ho jaey, wo uskey sath usey maarta hai to jin w Anas ke siwa mashriq w maghrib ke beech mojud her chiz us maar ko sunti hai, wo mitti ho jata hai, to phir rooh ko dobara is mein lota diya jata hai.'' , ( rawahu Ahmed (4 / 287 padhi. 18733 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 3212 , 4753 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 37 , 37  107 ( w Tabrani ( al-Mojam-al-Kabir 25 / 238, 240 padhi. 25) w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 395 ( ."
132,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai jab aap kisi qabr ke paas khadey hotey to wahan is qadr rotey ke aap ki dadhi tar ho jati , aap se puchha gaya, aap jannat aur jahannam ka tazkira kartey huey nahin rotey magar qabr ka zikr karkey rotey ho? to unhoney bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak qabr manazile-aakhirat mein se pehli manzil hai, pas agar us se bach gaya to uskey baad jo manaazil hain wo us se aasan tar hain, aur agar us se najat na hui to uskey baad jo manaazil hain wo us se ziyada sakht hain.'' raawi bayan kartey hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''maine qabr se ziyada sakht aur bura manzar kabhi nahin dekha.'' Tirmizi, ibne-Maja. aur Imam Tirmizi ne farmaya ye hadees gharib hai. rawahu Tirmizi ( 2308 ( w ibne-Maja ( 4267 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 371 , 4 / 330 , 331 ( ."
133,"Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maiyat ko dafn karney se farigh hotey to uskey paas khadey ho kar farmatey : '' apney bhai ke liye maghfirat talab karo, uskey liye ( sawal w jawab ke moqe par) Sabit qadmi ki darkhaast karo, kyonkey ab us se sawal kya jaeyga.'' rawahu Abu-Dawud ( 3221 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 37) ."
134,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kafir par , uski qabr mein , ninnanwey azdaha musallat kar diye jatey hain, wo qiyame-qiyamat tak usey dastey rahengey, agar un mein se eik azdaha zamin par phunk maar dey to zamin kisi qism ka sabza na ugaey.'' daarmi. Imam Tirmizi ne is tarah riwayat kya hai, unhoney ninnanwey ke bajaey sattar (azdaha) ka zikr kya hai. rawahu Darmi (1 / 331 padhi. 2818 ( w Tirmizi ( 2460 ( w anwaarus-sahifa (page 258 ( ."
135,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne wafat pai to ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath unke janaazey ke liye gaey, jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unki Namaz janaza padhi aur unhen qabr mein rakh kar ooper mitti dal di gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne tasbih bayan ki aur ham ne bhi taweel tasbih bayan ki, phir aapney Allahu-akbar padha to ham ne bhi Allahu-akbar padha , arz kya gaya, Allah ke Rasool ! aapney tasbih kyon bayan ki, phir aapney takbir bayan ki, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us Saleh bandey par uski qabr tang ho gaee thi, yahan tak ke Allah ne usey kushada kar diya .'' (rawahu Ahmed ( 3/ 360 padhi. 14934) (kitabul Jireh w tadeel 7 / 316 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 5 / 373 ( ."
136,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye (Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu)) wo shakhs hai jiski khatir arsh laraz gaya, uskey liye aasman ke darwazey khol diye gaey aur uski Namaze-janaza mein sattar hazar farishton ne shirkat ki, lekin usey bhi (qabr mein) dabaaya gaya phir unki qabr ko kushada kar diya gaya.'' rawahu Nasai (4 / 100, 101, 2058 ( ."
137,"Hazrat Asma binte-abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khutba irshad farmaney ke liye khadey huey to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne fitna qabr ka zikr farmaya jis mein aadmi ko aazmaya jaeyga, pas jab aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska zikr farmaya to musalman zor se roney lagey .'' Imam Nasaai ne izafa naqal kya hai : ye rona merey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka kalam samajhney ke beech haael ho gaya, jab unka ye ronaa aur shor thama to maine apney paas waley eik aadmi se kaha : Allah Taala tumhen barkat ata farmaai , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney kalam ke aakhir par kya farmaya? usney bataya : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey wahi ke zariey bataya gaya hai ke tum qabron mein fitnae-dajjaal ke qarib qarib aazamaye jaaogey.'' (Bukhari 1373 ( w Nasai (4 / 103 , 104, 2064 ( ."
138,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''jab maiyat ko qabr mein dakhil kya jata hai to usey Suraj aisey dikhaya jata hai jaisey wo qaribul-ghuroob ho, pas wo beth jata hai aur apni aankhen maltey huey kehta hai : mujhey chhod do main Namaz padh lun.'' (rawahu ibne-Maja (4272) w ibne-Hibban ( 779 ( w al-Behaqi (64) w ibne-Hibban ( 781 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 379 , 380 ( w fi majmaa-zawaaid (3 / 52 ( ."
139,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' maiyat qabr ki taraf jati hai to ( Saleh ( aadmi kisi qism ki ghabrahat ke baghair apni qabr mein beth jata hai, phir kaha jata hai, tum kis Deen par they? wo kahega Islam par , us se puchha jaeyga : ye aadmi kon they? wo kahega : Allah ke Rasool Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , wo Allah ki taraf se mojzat lekar hamarey paas tashrif laye to ham ne unki tasdeeq ki, us se puchha jaeyga : kya tum ne Allah ko dekha ? wo jawab dega : kisi ke liye ( duniya mein) Allah ko dekhna sahih w laaiq nahin, ( uskey baad) uskey liye jahannam ki taraf eik surakh kar diya jata hai, to wo uski taraf dekhta hai, ke jahannam ke baaz hissey baaz ko kha rahey hain, usey kaha jata hai, usey dekho jis se Allah ne tumhen bacha liya , phir uskey liye jannat ki taraf eik surakh kar diya jata hai to wo uski aur uski nematon ki ronaq w khoobsurti ko dekhta hai, to usey bataya jata hai ke ye tumhara maskan hai, tum yaqin par they, usi par tum faut huey aur inshaAllah tum usi par uthaey jaaogey, phir burey aadmi ko uski qabr mein bithaya jaeyga to wo bahut ghabraaya sa hoga, us se puchha jaeyga : tum kis Deen par they? to wo kahega : main nahin janta , phir us se puchha jaeyga : ye shakhs kon they? wo kahega : maine logon ko eik baat kartey huey suna to maine bhi wesey hi keh diya, (uskey baad) uskey liye jannat ki taraf eik surakh kar diya jaeyga, to wo uski aur uski nematon ki ronaq w khoobsurti ko dekhega , to usey kaha jaeyga : usko dekho jisey Allah ne tum se door kar diya, phir uskey liye jahannam ki taraf eik surakh kar diya jaeyga to wo usey dekhega ke uska baaz hissey baaz ko kha raha hai, usey kaha jaeyga ye tera thikana hai, to shak par tha, usi par faut hua aur inshaAllah usi par uthaya jaeyga.'' rawahu ibne-Maja ( 4268 ( ."
140,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney hamarey is Amr ( Deen ( mein koi aisa kaam jari kya jo ke is mein nahin wo mardud hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 2697 w Muslim ."
141,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamdo-sanaa aur salaat w salam ke baad, sab se behtareen kalam, Allah ki kitab hai, aur behtareen tariqa Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka tariqa hai, bad-tareen umur (baton) wo hain jo naey jari kiye jaeyn, aur her bidat gumrahi hai.'' rawahu Muslim w Nasai ( 3/ 189, 188 padhi. 1579 ( ."
142,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' teen qism ke log Allah ko sakht naa-pasandida hain, Haram mein zulm w na-insafi karney wala, Islam mein, jahiliyat ka tariqa talash karney wala aur badi jiddojehad ke baad kisi musalman ko nahaq qatl karney wala.'' Bukhari 6882 ( ."
143,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri sari ummat jannat mein jaeygi bajuz us shakhs ke jisney inkar kya. '' arz kya gaya, kis ne inkar kya? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne meri itaat ki wo jannat mein jaeyga aur jisney meri nafarmani ki goya usney inkar kar diya.'' (Bukhari 7280 ( ."
144,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, kuch farishtey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye, aap so rahey they, unhoney kaha : tumharey us sathi ki eik misal hai, wo misal unke samney bayan kar do, un mein se baaz farishton ne kaha : wo to soey huey hain, jabkey baaz ne kaha : be-shak aankhen soi hui hain lekin dil bedaar hai, pas unhoney kaha : unki misal us shakhs jaisi hai jisney eik ghar banaya , is mein dasterkhaan lagaya aur eik daee ko bheja , pas jis shakhs ne daee ki dawat ko qubul kar liya wo ghar mein dakhil hoga aur dasterkhaan se khana bhi khayega , aur jisney daaee ki dawat ko qubul na kya wo ghar mein dakhil hua na dasterkhaan se khana khaya , phir unhoney kaha : uski ( mazeed ( wazahat kerdo taake wo usey samajh saken, phir un mein se kisi ne kaha ke wo to soey huey hain aur baaz ne kaha : aankh soi hui hai aur dil bedaar hai, pas unhoney kaha : ghar , jannat hai, daee , Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain. pas jis shakhs ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki itaat ki to usney Allah ki itaat ki aur jisney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki nafarmani ki to usney Allah ki nafarmani ki, aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ke darmiyan farq karney waley hain.'' (Bukhari 7281 ( ."
145,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, teen log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ibadat ke mutalliq poochhney ke liye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki azwaj (jodey) mutahraat ke paas aaye , jab unhen uskey mutalliq bataya gaya, to goya unhoney usey kam mehsus kya, chunanche unhoney kaha : hamari Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kya nisbat ? Allah ne to unki agli pichli tamam khataeyn maaf farma di hain, un mein se eik ne kaha : main to hamesha sari raat Namaz padhunga . doosrey ne kaha : main din ke waqt hamesha roza rakhunga aur iftaar nahin karunga aur teesrey ne kaha : main aurton se ijtinab karunga aur main kabhi shaadi nahin karunga . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas aaye aur puchha : tum wo log ho jinhon ne is tarah, is tarah kaha hai, Allah ki qasam! main tum se ziyada Allah se darta hun aur tum se ziyada taqwa rakhta hun, lekin main roza bhi rakhta hun aur iftaar bhi karta hun, raat ko Namaz padhta hun aur sota bhi hun aur main aurton se shaadi bhi karta hun, pas jo shakhs meri sunnat se munh pherey wo mujh se nahin .'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 5053 w Muslim ."
146,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne koi kaam kya, phir aapney is mein rukhsat de-di to kuch logon ne rukhsat ko qubul karney se ijtinab kya, pas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko us barey mein pata chala to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khutba irshad farmaya , Allah ki hamd bayan ki, phir farmaya : '' logon ko kya ho gaya ke jo kaam main karta hun wo us se door rehtey hain, Allah ki qasam! main Allah ke mutalliq un se ziyada janta hun, aur us se un se ziyada darta hun.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6101 w Muslim ."
147,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina tashrif laye to wo (ehle-Madina ( khajuron ki pewandkari kya kartey they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne puchha : ''tum kya kartey ho?'' unhoney arz kya : ham aisey hi kartey aa rahey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar tum (pewandkaari) na karo to shayad tumharey liye behtar ho.'' unhoney aisa karna chhod diya to us se paidawar kam ho gaee. raawi bayan kartey hain, unhoney uskey mutalliq aap se baat ki to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main eik insan hun, jab main tumhen tumharey Deen ke kisi mamley ke barey main tumhen hukm dun to uski taameel karo, aur jab main apni raey se kisi chiz ke mutalliq tumhen koi hukm dun to main eik insan hun.'' rawahu Muslim ."
148,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri aur jis chiz ke sath Allah ne mujhey Nabi banakar bheja hai uski misal, us shakhs jaisi hai jo kisi qom ke paas aaya aur usney kaha : meri qom! maine apni aakhon se lashkar dekha hai aur main wazeh aur haqeeqi taur par aagah karney wala hun, lihaza tum jaldi se bachaaw kar lo, pas uski qom ka eik giroh uski baat maan kar sare-shaam itminan ke sath rawana ho gaya, aur wo bach gaya, jabkey unke eik giroh ne us shakhs ki baat ko jhutlaya aur apni jagah par datey rahey to subh hotey hi us lashkar ne un par dhaawa bol diya aur unhen mukammal taur par khatam kar diya, pas ye us shakhs ki misal hai jisney meri itaat ki aur meri laee hui shariyat ki ittiba ki, aur us shakhs ki misal hai jisney meri nafarmani ki aur merey laye huey haq ko jhutlaya.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 7283 w Muslim ."
149,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri misal us shakhs ki si hai jisney aag jalaai, pas jab us ( aag ( ne apney ird-gird ko roshan kar diya to parwaney aur aag mein girney waley keedey-makodey waghera is mein girna shuru ho gaey, aur wo shakhs unhen rokney laga lekin wo bazor is mein girney lagey, pas main tumhen kamar se pakad kar aag se rok raha hun jabkey tum bazor usi mein gir rahey ho.'' ye Bukhari ki riwayat hai aur Muslim ki riwayat bhi isi tarah hai aur uskey aakhir mein hai, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri aur tumhari misal is tarah hai ke main tumhen kamar se pakad kar aag se bacha raha hun, aag se bach kar meri taraf aa jaao, aag se bach kar meri taraf aa jaao, lekin tum mujh se bazor is mein gir rahey ho.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 6483 w Muslim ."
150,"Hazrat Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne jo hidayat aur ilm de-kar mujhey Nabi banakar bheja hai, wo kisi zamin par barasney wali moosladhar barish ki tarah hai, pas us zamin ka eik tukda bahut achcha tha, usney pani ko qubul kya aur usney bahut sa ghaas aur sabza ugaya, aur us zamin ka kuch tukda sakht tha, usney pani ko rok liya, pas Allah ne uskey zariey logon ko fayeda pahunchaya, logon ne khud piya, janwaron ko pilaya aur aab paashi ki, jabkey zamin ka eik tukda saaf chatiyal tha, wahan barish hui to wo pani rokti hai na sabza ugati hai, pas yehi misal us shakhs ki hai jisey Allah ke Deen mein samajh bojh ata ki gaee, aur Allah ne jo taalimaat de-kar mujhey Nabi banakar bheja un se usey faeyda pahunchaya, pas usney khud seekha aur dusron ko sikhaya, aur yehi us shakhs ki misal hai jisney ( az-raahe-takabbur) uski taraf sar na uthaya aur Allah ne jo hidayat de-kar mujhey Nabi banakar bheja usey qubul na kya.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 79 w Muslim ."
151,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''Allah hi wo zaat hai jisney aap par ye kitab nazil ki, uski baaz aayaten saaf wazeh hain aur mohkam hain.'' aur yahan tak tilawat farmaai : ''aur waz w nasihat ko sirf wohi log samajhtey hain jo aql mand hain.'' to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab to dekhay.'' jabkey Muslim ki riwayat mein hai : ''jab tum aisey logon ko dekho jo mukhtalif maana ki mutahammil aayaat talash kartey hain, to wo aisey log hain jinka Allah ne (dilon mein kaji rakhney waley) naam rakha hai, to tum un se bacho.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 4547 w Muslim."
152,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, main subh sawerey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, raawi bayan kartey hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne do aadmiyon ki aawaz suni jo ke kisi aayat ke barey mein jhagad rahey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ghussey ki haalat mein hamarey paas tashrif laye ghussey ke aasaar aapke chehrey par numaya they, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum se pehli qomen kitab mein ikhtilaf karney ki wajeh se halak huin.'' rawahu Muslim."
153,"Hazrat Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' musalmanon ke haq mein wo musalman sabse bada mujrim hai jisney kisi aisi chiz ke barey mein (apney Nabi sey) puchha jo pehley haram nahin thi, lekin uskey daryaft karney ki wajeh se usey haram kar diya gaya.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 7289 w Muslim."
154,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aakhiri daur mein faraib kaar jhootey log hongey, wo tumharey paas aisi ahadis laaeyngey jo tum ne na suni hongi na tumharey aaba ne, pas apney aap ko un se aur unhen apney aap se door rakho, taake wo tumhen gumrahi aur fitney mein mubtala na kar den.'' rawahu Muslim ."
155,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, ehle-kitab Torah Ibrani zaban mein padha kartey they aur ehle-Islam ke liye Arbi zaban mein uski tafseer bayan kya kartey they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ehle-kitab ki tasdeeq karo na takzeeb , balke kaho : ham Allah par aur jo hamari taraf nazil kya gaya is par eman laye .'' Bukhari 7542 ( ."
156,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aadmi ke jhoota honey ke liye bas yehi kafi hai ke wo her suni sunai baat ( tehqiq kiye baghair ( bayan kar dey .'' rawahu Muslim ."
157,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne mujh se pehley jis Nabi ko bheja to us Nabi ke uski ummat mein kuch muaawin aur kuch aam sathi hotey hain, wo uski sunnat ko qubul kartey aur uskey hukm ki ittiba kartey hain, phir unke baad burey ja-nashin aa jaeyngey wo aisi baaten karengey jis par unka amal nahin hoga aur aisey kaam karengey jinka unhen hukm nahin diya gaya hoga, pas jo shakhs apney haath ke sath un se jihad kerega wo momin hai, jo apni zaban ke sath un se jihad kerega wo momin hai, aur jo dil se un se jihad kerega to wo bhi momin hai, aur uskey baad raai ke daney ke barabar bhi eman nahin.'' rawahu Muslim ."
158,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs hidayat ki taraf dawat dey to usey bhi us hidayat ki ittiba karney walon ki misl sawab milega, aur ye unke ajr mein koi kami nahin kerega, aur jo shakhs kisi gumrahi ki taraf dawat dey to usey bhi us gumrahi ki ittiba karney walon ki misl gunah milega, aur ye unke gunah mein koi kami nahin kerega.'' rawahu Muslim ."
159,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Islam ajnabiyat ke aalim mein shuru hua , aur an-qareeb usi haalat mein lot jaeyga jaisey shuru hua, pas ajnabiyon (jinhon ne Islam ke ibtidaai (shuruati) daur aur aakhiri daur mein Islam ka sath diya) ke liye khushkhabri hai.'' rawahu Muslim ."
160,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak eman Madina ki taraf simat aaeyga jis tarah sanp apney bil ki taraf simat aata hai.'' muttafaq aleh, Bukhari 1876 w Muslim. ham inshaAllah taala Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadees : ( ذرونی ما ترکتکم ( kitabul-manaasik» mein aur Muawiya w Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadisein : ( (la yazalu man ummati) (aur ( (wala yazalu taaifa man ummati) ( baab sawab haazihil-umma» mein zikr karengey ."
161,"Hazrat Rabeea Jarshi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat main eik farishta hazir hua , aur aap se arz kya gaya : aapki aankhen soi hui hon (kisi aur taraf na dekhen (aap ke kaan tawajjoh se suntey hon aur aap ka dil samajhta ho, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri aankhen so gaeen , merey kaan ghor se suntey rahey aur mera dil samajhta raha .'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey kaha gaya : kisi sardar ne koi ghar banaya , is mein dasterkhaan lagaya aur kisi dawat deney waley ko bheja , pas jis shakhs ne daee ki dawat ko qubul kar liya , wo ghar mein dakhil hua , khana khaya aur wo sardar us se khush ho gaya, aur jis shakhs ne daee ki dawat qubul na ki to wo na ghar mein dakhil hua na khana khaya aur sardar bhi is par naraz hua.'' aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah, sardar hai, Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) daee hain, ghar se murad Islam aur dasterkhaan se murad jannat hai.'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 711) ."
162,"Hazrat abu Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tum mein se kisi ko apni musnad par tek lagaey huey na paaon ke uskey paas mera koi Amr aaye , jiskey mutalliq maine hukm diya ho ya maine us se mana kya ho, to wo shakhs yun kahey : main (usey) nahin janta , ham ne jo kuch Allah ki kitab mein paya, ham uski ittiba karengey.'' (rawahu Ahmed (6 /8 padhi. 24362 , w Tirmizi ( 2663 ( w Abu-Dawud ( 605 ( w ibne-Maja (13) w al-Behaqi fi dalaailunnubuwa (1 / 25, 6 / 549 ( w ibne-Hibban (13) w al-Hakim (1 / 108, 109) ."
163,"Hazrat Miqdad bin Maadi Karb (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' sun lo , mujhey Quran aur uskey sath uski misl ata ki gaee hai, sun lo , qarib hai ke koi pet bhara hua shakhs apni musnad par yun kahey : tum us Quran ko lazim pakdo pas tum jo chiz is mein halal paao usey halal samjho aur tum jo chiz usmein haram paao to usey haram samjho , halanke Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jis chiz ko haram qarar diya hai wo aisey hi hai jaisey Allah ne haram qarar diya hai, sun lo , paaltu gadhey , kachli waley darindey aur zimmi ki giri padi koi chiz, siwaey iske ke wo khud us se be niaz ho jaey, tumharey liye halal nahin, aur jo shakhs kisi qom ke yahan padaaw daley to un logon par lazim hai ke wo uski ziyaafat karen, aur agar wo uski ziyaafat na karen, to phir usey haq hasil hai ke wo apni ziyaafat ke barabar un se wasul karey.'' rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 4604 ( w daarmi (1 / 144  592 ( w ibne-Maja (12) w ibne-Hibban (97) . Darmi ne bhi isi tarah riwayat kya hai, aur isi tarah ibne-Maja ne bhi riwayat kya hai."
164,"Hazrat Irbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey huey aur farmaya : ''kya tum mein se koi apni musnad par tek laga kar ye guman karta hai ke Allah ne sirf wohi kuch haram qarar diya hai jis ka zikr Quran mein hai, sun lo ! Allah ki qism ! maine bhi kuch chizon ke barey mein hukm diya hai, waaz w nasihat ki aur kuch chizon se mana kya, bila-shuba wo bhi Quran ki misl hain balke us se bhi ziyada hai, be-shak Allah ne tumharey liye halal nahin kya ke tum bila ijazat ehle-kitab ( zimmiyon (ke gharon mein dakhil ho jaao aur jab tak wo tumhen jiziya detey rahen , unki khawatin ko maarna aur unke phal khana tumharey liye halal nahin .'' Abu-Dawud, iski sanad mein Ash-as bin Shoba Mussisi raawi hai jis par kalam kya gaya hai. rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 3050 ( ."
165,"Hazrat Irbaz bin Saariya (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, eik roz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamen Namaz padhaai , phir aapney apna rukh anwar hamari taraf kya to eik badey baleegh andaz mein hamen waaz w nasihat farmaai jis se aankhen aansuon se tar ho gaeen aur dil dar gaey, eik aadmi ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! ye to alwidaai naseehatein malum hoti hain, pas aap hamen wasiyat farmaeyn, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhen Allah ka taqwa ikhtiyar kerney, sunney aur itaat karney ki wasiyat karta hun chahey wo ( ameer ( Habshi ghulam ho, kyonkey tum mein se jo shakhs merey baad zinda rahega wo bahut ikhtilaf dekhega , pas tum par meri aur hidayat yafta khulfaae-raashideen ki sunnat lazim hai, pas tum us se tamassuk ikhtiyar karo aur daadhiyon ke sath usey pakad lo, aur Deen mein naey kaam jari karney se bacho , kyonkey Deen mein her naya kaam bidat hai aur her bidat gumrahi hai.'' Ahmed, Abu-Dawud, Tirmizi, ibne-Maja . albatta Imam Tirmizi aur Imam ibne-Maja ne Namaz ka zikr nahin kya. rawahu Ahmed (4 / 126 , 127 padhi. 17275 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 4607 ( w Tirmizi ( 2676 ( w ibne-Maja (43) w ibne-Hibban (102) w al-Hakim (1 / 95 , 96 ( ."
166,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hamarey liye eik khat khincha , phir farmaya : ''ye Allah ki raah hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey daain baain kuch khat kheenchey , aur farmaya : ''ye aur raahen hain, aur un mein se her raah par eik shetan hai jo us raah ki taraf bulata hai.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''ye meri sidhi raah hai, pas uski ittiba karo.'' rawahu Ahmed (1 / 435 padhi. 4142 ( w Nasai ( fil-kubra 194 ( w ibne-Hibban ( 1741 , 1742 ( w al-Hakim ( 2 / 317 ( w ibne-Maja (11) ."
167,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi shakhs momin nahin ho sakta yahan tak ke uski khaahishat meri laee hui shariyat ke tabey ho jaeyn '' Imam Baghwi ne Sharahus-sunnah mein isey riwayat kya hai. Imam Nauwi ne Arbaeen mein farmaya : ye hadees sahih hai aur ham ne isey kitabul-Haj mein sahih sanad ke saath riwayat kya hai. (rawahu fi Sharahus-sunnah (1 / 212 , 213, 104) w Nauwi fi al-arbaiin (41) ."
168,"Hazrat Bilal bin Haris Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney meri kisi aisi sunnat ko zinda kya, jisey merey baad tarak kar diya gaya, to usey bhi, is par amal karney walon ke barabar sawab milega aur unke ajr mein koi kami nahin hogi, aur jisney bidat w gumrahi ko jaari kya jisey Allah aur uskey Rasool pasand nahin kartey, to usey bhi utna hi gunah milega jitna is par amal karney walon ko milega aur unke gunahon mein koi kami nahin hogi.'' rawahu Tirmizi (2677) w ibne-Maja (209)."
169,isey Tirmizi ne riwayat kya hai aur ibne-Maja ne ye riwayat Kasir bin Abdullah bin Amr an (an) Abi an (an) Jadda ke tareeq se bayan ki hai. rawahu ibne-Maja ( 210 ( .
170,"Hazrat Amr bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Deen hijaaz ki taraf is tarah simat jaeyga jis tarah sanp apney bil ki taraf simat jata hai, aur Deen Hijaaz mein is tarah mehfooz hoga jis tarah pahadi bakri pahad ki choti par panah leti hai, be-shak Deen ka aaghaz ajnabiyat ke aalim mein hua aur wo an-qareeb usi haalat mein lot jaeyga jaisey shuru hua , aisey ajnabiyon ke liye khushkhabri hai, aur yehi wo log hain jo meri sunnat ki islah w ehya karengey jisey logon ne merey baad kharab kar diya hoga.'' (rawahu Tirmizi ( 2630 ( ."
171,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''meri ummat par aisa waqt aaeyga jaisey Bani-Israel par aaya tha, aur wo unke jaisa honey mein aisey hoga jaisey joota jootey ke barabar hota hai, yahan tak ke agar un mein se kisi ne apni maa se elania bad-kari ki hogi to meri ummat mein bhi aisa karney wala shakhs hoga, beshak Bani-Israel 72 firqon mein taqseem huey aur meri ummat 73 firqon mein taqseem hogi, eik millat ke siwa baqi sab jahannam mein hongey.'' Sahaba ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ! wo eik millat kon si hai? aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis par mein aur merey Sahaba hain.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2641 ( ."
172,"Hazrat Ahmed aur Abu-Dawood mein Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) riwayat mein hai : '' bahattar jahannam mein jaeyngey aur eik jannat mein jaeyga, aur an-qareeb meri ummat mein aisey log zahir hongey un mein ye bad-duaa is tarah saraayat kar jaeyngi jis tarah baawley kuttey ka asar katey huey shakhs ke rag w reshey mein saraayat kar jata hai.'' rawahu Ahmed (4 / 102 ,17061 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 4597 ( ."
173,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala meri ummat ko .'' ya farmaya : '' Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki ummat ko gumrahi par jama nahin kerega aur Allah Taala ka haath jamaat par hai aur jo shakhs jamaat se juda hua wo jahannam mein alag dala jaeyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2167 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 116, 399)."
174,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''sawaade-aazam (badi jamaat) ki ittiba karo, kyonkey jo alag hua, wo jahannam mein dala jaeyga.'' Imam ibne-Maja ne ye hadees Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai. (rawahu al-Hakim fi al-mustadrak (1 / 115, 116) w ibne-Maja ( 3950 ( ."
175,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : '' beta ! agar to subh w Sham us haalat mein kar sakey ke tumharey dil mein kisi ke liye bad-khuwahi na ho to aisa kar.'' phir farmaya : ''beta! ye tarze-amal meri sunnat hai, aur jisney meri sunnat se mohabbat ki to usney mujh se mohabbat ki, aur jisney mujh se mohabbat ki to wo jannat mein merey sath hoga.'' (rawahu Tirmizi ( 2678 ( ."
176,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne meri ummat ke fasad ke waqt meri sunnat par amal kya to uskey liye so Shahid ka sawab hai.'' ( al-Behaqi fi Zuhud ( 209 ( w ibn Adi ( 2 / 739 ( w Tabrani ( 5410 ( majmaa Zawaaid (1 / 172 , 3 / 208 ( al-anwaar lil-Baghwi bit-tahqeeq ( 1237 ( ."
177,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas aaye to unhoney kaha : ham yahood se kuch tajjub angez baaten suntey hain, kya aap ijazat marahmat farmatey hain ke ham un mein se baaz likh liya karen, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum bhi yahood w nasara ki tarah (apney Deen ke barey mein) hairaan ho, jabkey main tumharey paas saaf aur wazeh Deen lekar aaya hun. agar Musa (Alaihissalam) bhi zinda hotey to unke liye bhi meri ittiba ke siwa kisi aur chiz ki ittiba jayez na hoti .'' (rawahu Ahmed ( 3 / 387 padhi. 15223 ( al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan (176) w Darni (1 / 115, 116, 441)."
178,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne halal khaya , sunnat ke muwaafiq amal kya aur log uski shar-angeziyon se mehfooz rahey to wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.'' kisi aadmi ne arz kya : Allah ke Rasool ! is daur main to is tarah ke bahut se log hain, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' aur merey baad ke daur mein bhi hongey.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 252 ( w al-Hakim (4 / 104) ."
179,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum us daur mein ho ke tum mein se jisney ehkame-sharia ke daswein hissey par amal na kya to wo halak ho jaeyga, phir eik aisa daur aaeyga ke unmein se jisney ehkamaate-sharia ke daswein hissey par amal kar liya to wo najat pa jaeyga.'' rawahu Tirmizi ( 2267 ( ."
180,"Hazrat abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi qom hidayat yafta honey ke baad gumrahi ikhtiyar kar leti hai to bahami (aapsi) jhagda unka kaam bin jata hai.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''wo aap se ye baaten mehaz jhagda paida karney ke liye kartey hain balke ye log hain hi jhagdalu.'' rawahu Ahmed (5 / 252 padhi. 22517, 5 / 256 padhi. 22558 ( w Tirmizi ( 3253 ( w ibne-Maja (68) w al-Hakim (2 / 448 ( ."
181,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : '' apney aap ko mashaqqat mein na dala karo, warna Allah bhi tumhen mashaqqat mein dal dega , kyonkey eik qom ne apney aap par sakhti ki to Allah ne bhi un par sakhti ki, yahood w Nasara ki ibadat gaahon mein ye sakhtiyan unhi ki baaqiyaat hain.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aayat tilawat farmaai : ''rehbaniyat unhoney khud ejaad ki thi ham ne usey un par farz nahin kya tha.'' ( rawahu Abu-Dawood ( 4906 ( Bukhari fi taareekhul-Kabir (4 / 94) ."
182,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Quran paanch umur (baton) ke mutalliq nazil hua, halal w haram, mohkam w mutashabeh aur Amsaal. tum halal ko halal aur haram ko haram samjho, mohkam par amal karo aur mutashabeh par eman laao aur Amsaal (pehli ummaton ke waqiyat) se ibrat hasil karo.'' ye masaabeh ke alfaz hain. Behaqi ne shobil-emaan mein in alfaz se naqal kya hai : ''halal par amal karo, haram se ijtinab karo aur mohkam ki ittiba karo.'' (rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 2293 ( ."
183,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Amr teen qism ke hain, eik Amr wo hai jiski rushdo-bhalai wazeh hai, pas uski ittiba karo, eik Amr wo hai jiski gumrahi wazeh hai pas us se ijtinab karo aur eik Amr wo hai jiskey mutalliq ikhtilaf kya gaya hai, pas usey Allah azz-w-jall ke supurd karo.'' (rawahu Ahmed ( ) w Tabrani fil-Kabir ( 10/ 386 padhi. 10774 ( ."
184,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak shetan insan ke liye bhediya hai jaisey bakriyon ke liye bhediya hota hai, wo alag honey wali, door janey waley aur eik janib honey wali bakri ko pakadta hai. pas tum ghaatiyon ( alag alag honey ( se bacho aur tum jamaate-aamma ko lazim pakad lo.'' rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 243 padhi. 22458 , 5 / 232 padhi. 22379 ( ."
185,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney jamaat se baalisht barabar alehdgi ikhtiyar ki to usney apni gardan se Islam ki rassi (yani pabandi ( utaar di.'' ( rawahu Ahmed ( 5 / 180 padhi. 21894 ( w Abu-Dawood ( 4758 ( w ibne-abi Aasim fis-sunnah ( 1053 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 117 ( w Tirmizi ( 2763 ( ."
186,"Hazrat Malik bin Anas (Raziallahu anhu) mursal riwayat bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tum mein do chizen chhod kar ja raha hun, pas jab tak tum un dono par amal kartey rahogey to kabhi gumrah nahin hogey , (yani ( Allah ki kitab aur uskey Rasool ki sunnat .'' ( rawahu Malik fil-Mauta ( 2 / 899 padhi. 1727 ( w al-Hakim (1 / 93 padhi. 317 ( ."
187,"Hazrat Ghuzaif bin Haris Samali (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab koi qom bidat ejaad karti hai to usi ki misl sunnat utha li jati hai, pas sunnat par amal karna bidat ejaad karney se behtar hai.'' rawahu Ahmed (4 / 105 padhi. 17095 ( ."
188,"Hazrat Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, jab koi qom apney Deen mein koi bidat ejaad karti hai to Allah uski misl unki sunnat chheen leta hai, phir wo usey roze-qiyamat tak unki taraf nahin lautata.'' (rawahu Darmi (1 / 45 padhi. 99) ."
189,"Hazrat Ibrahim bin Maisra (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne kisi bidati ki tazeem w nusrat ki to usney Islam ke giraaney par muaawinat ki .'' ( rawahu al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 9464 ( ."
190,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne Allah ki kitab ki taalim hasil ki, phir uskey mutabiq amal kya to Allah us shakhs ko duniya mein gumrahi se bachata hai aur qiyamat ke din usey hisab ki takleef se bachaeyga.'' aur eik riwayat mein hai, ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya , jis shakhs ne Allah ki kitab ki iqtida (pairvi) ki to wo duniya mein gumrah hoga na aakhirat mein takleef uthaeyga, phir us aayat ki tilawat farmaai : ''jo shakhs meri hidayat ki perwi kerega wo gumrah hoga na takleef mein padega.'' (rawahu rizeen ( ) w abdur-Razzaaq ( 3 / 382 ح۶۰۳۳ ( w ibne-abi Sheba ( 10 / 467 , 468 padhi. 29946 , 13 / 371 , 372 padhi. 34770 ( w al-Hakim ( 2 / 381 padhi. 3438 ( w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 2029 ( ."
191,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ne siraate-mustaqeem ki misal bayan farmaai , ke raastey ke dono taraf do diwaarein hain, un mein darwazey khuley huey hain aur darwazon par pardey latak rahey hain, raastey ke sirey par eik daee hai, wo keh raha hai, sidhey chaltey jaao , tedhey mat hona, aur uskey ooper eik aur daee hai, jab koi shakhs un darwazon mein se kisi chiz ko kholney ka irada karta hai to wo kehta hai : tum par afsos hai, usey mat kholo, kyonkey agar tum ne usey khol diya to tum is mein dakhil ho jaaogey.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uski wazahat kartey huey farmaya : ''raasta Islam hai, khuley huey darwazey, Allah ki haram karda cheezein hain, latkey huey pardey, Allah ki hudood hain, raastey ke sirey par daee Quran hai, aur uskey ooper jo daee hai, wo her momin ke dil mein Allah ka waaiz hai.'' (rawahu rizeen) ."
192,"Hazrat Imam Ahmed, aur Behaqi ne Shobil-emaan mein Nawaas bin Samaan (Raziallahu anhu) se aur isi tarah Imam Tirmizi ne unhi se riwayat kya hai, albatta unhoney us se mukhtasar riwayat kya hai. ( rawahu Ahmed (4 / 182 , 183 7784 ( w al-Behaqi fi-Shobil-Emaan ( 7214 ( w Tirmizi ( 2859 ( ."
193,"Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : jo koi kisi shakhs ki raah apnana chahey to wo un logon ki raah apnaey jo faut ho chukey hain, kyonkey zinda shakhs fitney se mehfooz nahin raha , aur wo ( faut shuda log) Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sathi hain, wo is ummat ke behtareen afrad they, wo dil ke saaf , ilm mein gehrey aur takalluf w tasanno mein bahut kam they, Allah ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sohbat aur apney Deen ki iqaamat ke liye unhen muntakhab farmaya, pas unki fazilat ko pahchaano , unki baaton ki ittiba karo aur unke akhlaq w kirdaar ko apnaney ki taqat bhar koshish karo, kyonkey wo sidhi raah par they.'' rawahu rizeen."
194,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Torah ka eik nuskha lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya, Allah ke Rasool ! ye Torah ka nuskha hai, aap khamosh rahey, aur unhoney usey padhna shuru kar diya, jabkey Rasulullah ke chehre Mubarak ka rang badalney laga, abu-Bakar ne farmaya : gum karney wali tumhen gum paeyn, tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke rukh anwar ki taraf nahin dekh rahey, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak dekha to fauran kaha : main Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghazab se Allah ki panah chahta hun, main Allah ke rab honey, Islam ke Deen honey aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Nabi honey par razi hun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' us zaat ki qism jiskey haath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jaan hai. agar Musa (Alaihissalam) bhi tumharey samney aa jaeyn aur tum mujhey chhod kar unki ittiba karney lago to tum sidhi raah se gumrah ho jaaogey, aur agar wo zinda hotey aur wo meri nabuwat (ka zamana) pa letey to wo bhi meri hi ittiba kartey .'' rawahu Darmi (1 / 115 , 116, 441)."
195,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah ne farmaya : '' mera kalam , Allah ke kalam ko mansookh nahin kar sakta , jabkey Allah ka kalam merey kalam ko mansookh kar sakta hai aur aur Allah ka kalam eik doosrey ko mansookh kar sakta hai.'' rawahu Dar-Qutni (4 / 145 ( ."
196,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' hamari ahadis bhi eik doosrey ko mansookh kar deti hain. jis tarah Quran ka baaz hissey doosrey hissey ko mansookh kar deta hai. Dar-Qutni (4 / 145 ( ."
197,"Hazrat abu-Solba Khushni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' be-shak Allah ne faraaiz muqarrar kiye hain, unhen zaya na karo, usney hurumaat ko haram qarar diya hai, pas unke qarib na jaao aur Allah ne hudood mutayyan ki hain pas un se tajawuz na karo aur usney jantey-boojhtey kuch chizon se sukoot farmaya , pas unke mutalliq behes na karo.'' mazkura teeno ahadis ko Dar-Qutni ne bayan kya hai. rawahu Dar-Qutni (4 / 183 , 184 ( w al-Behaqi ( 10 / 12 , 13 ( ."
